\id ACT
\ide UTF-8
\h Nangen Nob Tomange
\toc1 Nangen Nob Tomange
\toc2 Nangen Nob Tomange
\toc3 act
\mt1 Nangen Nob Tomange
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Bifumero mi mulanyi kika, Theophilus in tok dikero Yesu ter makau la merange.
\v 2 Na nyime diye cii tumou yaken dii kwama. Wo kambo cine nob tomangeb cebo cidoweu yuwatangbeke.
\v 3 Kambo cinuwa dotangeri yadangu dorcero ciinen, ki yiromtinim dukce wo nyomkace. kume kwini naar ci dangu dorcero ciinene yi cii ker liyar kwamar
\v 4 Kambo ci yi kange cii yeri in yi cii, ciya dobre wursalima dila ciya ningtang nor Teero, woci yiki, “Kom nuwa fiye mi wiyeu”
\v 5 Yiti ki, cwerke man Yahaya yucinen mwembo kin wmom, dila ayukumen mwembo ki yuwa tangbeko wucakke, kume fo kutangbo”.
\v 6 Kambo cii wariyeri cin meco Kwama ki kwamawo mwa yilauti ki liyar Israila ka?
\v 7 Yi cii ki, a keno nakume nakom nyimom kan kenekowo kwama yo morbikwan durcereu.
\v 8 Dila kom yo bikwando cano yuwatangbe kwamako bou dor kumerdi, lana nyime kan yilam nob wabebkeb min mor wursalima kange mor yahudiya gwam kange samariya, yaken ciko cwile dor bitinere”.
\v 9 Ki kwama wo kwama Yesu tok kero birombem, kambo cito dii kwamatiyeri, dila cii tumco ciin yaken kico dii kwama, biloro yurangum co nuwece.
\v 10 Kambo cii to dikwama ciya kenti yeri, dang jang nubo yob tim kaci ki kulendo fuwor.
\v 11 Kom nabarubbo halili, yebwi kom tirangum fo komto dii kwamatiye? wuro Yesu yaken dii kwama, kambo kom tom yamcembeu dii kwamau ayilaunyo
\v 12 Kambo cii yilau bany Zaitun cii yoten yilau wursalima wuro bidom kange wursalimau, yam kume nukkune ki dimen.
\v 13 Kambo cii lameri, ciin yabken tiyak fiye cii yimtiyeu. ciin bi Bitrus, Yahaya, Yakubu, Andirawus, Filibus, Tomas Bartholomew, Matta, Yakubu bibwe Alfa Siman Yahuda bibwe Yakubu.
\v 14 Gwam ce ciin mwerkang dorceo win, kambo cii ca kaba ki kwob dilo. Matta, Maryamu wo bo Yesu kange kebcoba cii wari.
\v 15 Ki kume niwo Bitrus kweniti tiber kebceber, nubo kwini kwob toro kwini yob, yi cii.
\v 16 keb mibo nii inwi wo ticiinen kaba ciitam Yesu.
\v 17 Wifo morebe lan yom dike naceu dor dike cimaneu.
\v 18 Niwo tenum bitine ki kemero cifiyau mor nagen bwirantum nerer cero, cin yaru wi kidor fwercero wurom, yeicero coru kale.
\v 19 Nubo yimwi wursalima nuwam wo lacii cuwo fiyeco kin yicii “Akeldama” (Kiyiki fiye bwiyale).
\v 20 Wori cii mulange mor bifumer Zaburad Lafiyeceu ayilam kamlo adobeni ayifiyeco kange atum nangen cero.
\v 21 Nawori tamnyo win mor nubo wo wari kange bo ki kwama Yesu ma doka kange cerka ceko yeu, morebe.
\v 22 Terti ki yuka mu ngek Yahaya yakaken ciko kakukowa cii tumco binenneu yaken dii kwama a yilam, win morebe fiye tokka ker kwenkacek.
\v 23 Ciin dang nubo yob Yusufu woci choti ki Barsabbas, wotak ci cho dendo ki Justus kange Matthias.
\v 24 Ciin kwob dilo ciiki, kwama mo mun yob ner nubere. dan nyinen wo mu coke morece yobewo.
\v 25 Na tu nyi Yahuda fiye yahuda tiyangum meu yaken fiye”
\v 26 Ciin mer dacendo dor ciir, dacendo yardor Matiyas dila ciin kiyeti co mor nob tomangeb Sulombo yobeu.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Kambo kume fentikos co bouwori, kwarubce ciin mwerum fiye win.
\v 2 Nawo nawo diro kange wi dikwama na yuwako dur, yiram dim luweu cii yim wiyeu.
\v 3 labiyondo kange na biyen kiret layiron cilnenti dor.
\v 4 Ciin dimki yuwa tangbe kwama lacin ter tokka kereki nyini kangum kambo yuwa tangbe kwamako dang cinenneu.
\v 5 Ki kwama co Yahudawa kangum wi yim wursalima, nob kwamabo fo dorbitiner.
\v 6 Kambo cii nuwa diroweri, nubo gwam mwerum cii mor ciin nuwa nubo tikkan keroti kin yici.
\v 7 Ciin to diker nyimankar laciiki, kibi chom birombo kebo Galiliyawaka?
\v 8 manyi bi nuwa citi wiyak wuyakce cii tok nyowo cii bombotiye?
\v 9 Fisiyawa kange mediyawa kange Elimawa, kange Yahudawa kange Kafadokiya, mor Pontus kange Asia.
\v 10 Phrygia kange Pamphylia, mor Masar kange sunga libiya wo sur receu, kange fabubbo Roma.
\v 11 Yahudawa kange proselyte, cretans kange arabian, be nuwa tokkeroti kin nyibo dor nangebdo durembo kwama maneu.
\v 12 Gwam ciin nyimangi ciin yi bwiticeu, Yewo toktiye?
\v 13 Kan nyumbo buwocii ki, ciin diim ki nyom.
\v 14 Dila Bitrus kweni kange sulombo yobem, kundiro tok kerki “Nubo yahuda kange kom kwarub kom yim wursalima, kom nyimomwo, ko suwatuu ker mironin.
\v 15 Nubowo ci dimbo diye ki nyom kambo kom kwatiyeu, wori kene Teer na burice koni.
\v 16 dila won co dike toki ywel neneu nii ker dukumer.
\v 17 Kwama ki nyo a yilati cwile kume, man coru yuwatangbeko dor nuber, bi biyolokumeu bayilob kange natub ciyan tokker dukumer.
\v 18 Nyo tak dor caan yabmib bayilob kange natub, kikuke tindowe man corum yuwatangbe miko, laciyan tok ker dukumer.
\v 19 man madiker nyimakar dii kwama kange dor bitiner, bwiyale kange kira, kange yilom.
\v 20 kakokko an yilam kumtachile, chuwakko ayilam bwiyale nanyime kume durkowo kwamaceu nabou.
\v 21 an yilam woco den kwama an fiya fuloka.
\v 22 Nubo Israila kom cuwatuu kero birombonen. Yesu banzared niwo kwama nekom wuro kwama ma nangen durem more kume fiyeci wuyeu, nawo komki bwikom kanyimeu.
\v 23 Nii wo ciin neken co kan nage kange yobka kwama cii neken co kom keneu kang nubo yombo ker kwamareu cii twalum ki kuldange.
\v 24 Wo kwama kungun co cokeinen twirak buwareko cinenneu, wo mani natamce.
\v 25 Dauda tokker donce ki kwamati kami ngir wori cin wi cunga kange cattiyeri katin mikannge.
\v 26 Lanyori nermiro ma fuwer nerti biyel miro ti bilenke. Labwimiu anyi kibi kwan.
\v 27 mani mu minang dumemitiwi manu do wucakke mweti a to fuyenin.
\v 28 Dang men nure dumeu, nawo tikob mwebo adim yeti ki fuwor nereu.
\v 29 Keb mibo man yikom ker nyanglang dor Tee Dauda: buyam ciin furomco dila tuweceu wifo wari kange bo di duwenokowo.
\v 30 Nyori wori cin nii ker dukumer dila nyimom kwama macinen nor kiweri ki, mor tuwe luwe mwe man yoti kange kutile liyar cero nen.
\v 31 Cin tou dikero wo dila tok kero dor kwentka kriti mani cii ma bilankiya kange co fiye morka dumek, bwiceu tobo fuyeka.
\v 32 Wo Yesu wo kwama kunco wuro wuyakbe bin nyimom.
\v 33 Nyori kambo cii kunco yaken kanka cattiyere kwamau dila nyo mor yuwa tangbe kwamako fiye Tee wiyeu coci corbinenneu wo komtoti takri kom nuwatiyeu.
\v 34 Dauda kwibo dii dila yiki kwama dila toki kwama nyi Teeluwemiu yiken kango cattiyeremi.
\v 35 Dila man yoken nob kiyeb mwebbo diker fuwaka namwek.
\v 36 La nyori, naweu lo Israila a nyomom kang Yesu wo cii kulkenen kwama yoken co kwama kange kritti.
\v 37 Cii nuwa nyori la kwerci nercer cii yi Bitrus kange tannineu nob tomangeb cebo. “Keb mibo ye ba matiye?”.
\v 38 La Bitrus yiki Kom dubom bwiranker kumero nakom yumbom, mor den Yesu kristi na wam bwirangker kumero tak kan yo neken yuwatangbek kwama ko.
\v 39 Wor noro ki kom kange bibeyo lokume, kwarub kange birombo kutaneu, gwam nubo tee be kwama a coutiyeu”.
\v 40 Kero ducce cii ne warke naci chuwaci ki cii nayiki, “Kom fulom dor kumero mor kalewo bwiranyeu.”
\v 41 Lakom yo kercero nacii yukumen mwembo, kume ciin fiyaten nubo cabten bikate taar.
\v 42 Lacii ca kaba ki merangka no tomangebbo kange yimbo winneu, mor caka tiilita kange dilo.
\v 43 Taito bou dorcir la cin ma diker nyimankaro kan ya yiromboti kila fiye nob tomangebo wiyeu.
\v 44 Gwam nubo nebilinker cii mwerum fiye win diker ciro na bwiticiyece.
\v 45 La cii tokang dike cii cikeu kang dike cii ciko wiyakkeu laci kabkange dong dong kange cii cwitiyeu cii cikeu.
\v 46 Fini win cii ca kabati ki nero mor lo wabe cii kiyan tiilita lonice cii kabkang caritoti bwitice mor fuwor nerer kange kungne necer.
\v 47 Cii caklang kwamati ciin fiya yokati kabum nubem gwam. kwama cob cinenten nubowuro fiya dumetiyeu.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Na wo Bitrus kange Yuwanna yakenti kuwabe kwama ki kwma kwobka dilo kan keno taar.
\v 2 Ni kange kilen ci bouciko nyo cii ki tuu kwaticobak nabou ciko nyilo kuwabka wo cii coti ki yoryoreu ki ken kim nubo dokenti mor kuwabi kwamau.
\v 3 To Bitrus kange Yuwanna doken mor kuwabi kwama, kenci luma nerer.
\v 4 Bitrus kange Yuwanna ciin cii cinenten kanuwe Bitrus yiki, “To nyo”.
\v 5 kilendo to cii kwatiki keno can fiya diker ciinen na.
\v 6 Dila Bitrus yiki cilfa kange mwiin, kange nai mi mani ciko, Dila dike min cikeu co manetiye. mor den Yesu kristi bwe Nazaret, ya yam”.
\v 7 Bitrus tam kanceko cattiyero kunco nawo nawo naniceu kange kutile naniceu fiyam bikwan.
\v 8 La kilendo kweni tari teryambo doken kuwabe kange Bitrus kange Yuwanna citi fuwai citi mwai ci ne kwama durkoti.
\v 9 Nubo tou co yayambo, caklang kwama.
\v 10 Ciin nyimom ki coni kiyire nyilo lo wabi yoryori la ciin dim ki nyimanka ki dikero bweyeu.
\v 11 Kambo ci tamki kang Bitrus kange Yuwanna nubo kwarub kutauten ciinen, cunnge Tangilang sulemanu Cii ti nyimangi kambo ken.
\v 12 Kambo Bitrus to nyeri in cinya nubow kom nubo Israila yebwi kom nyimang tiye? Yebwi kom cii nyinenten duwenye, mumi nyo nyi dokco co ciya yambo tiye kibi kwan dorer nyer kaka'a ki luma nyak?
\v 13 Kwama Ibrahim, kange Ishaku, kange yakubu kwama teebnyebe ne bwe cannya ceu durko Yesu co kom koweu takri ka nekenco kabum Bilatus wo noncwi naci nyam kang cinen neu.
\v 14 Kom ko niwo wucakeu nii lumake nyori lakomki a nya kumen kang niwo twal dore.
\v 15 Kom twalum niwo ne dumetiyeu, wo kwama kunnyu tuweu, nye nyim nob neka bilenker dikero bwiyenen.
\v 16 na weu, bilenker ki dencer niwo kom toti takri kom nyimom kinco dende wo cifiya bikwaneu. Bileng mor Yesu neco luma ceko cike cok, kabum kumem.
\v 17 Kebmibbo min nyimom kom mayeu mor bwini nyomka, kambo liyab kumeb maneu.
\v 18 Dila gwam dikero kwama tokanyi nob tomangeb dukumemcembou ki, Kristi an nuwa dotange landim.
\v 19 Nawo yeu kom dubom bwirang ker kumero kom yilau dabe wam bwirang ke kumeu, wori kwama ywelkako fiye kwama wiyeu lam.
\v 20 Na cii tomuu ki kristi wuro cii yokumen lan, Yesu.
\v 21 Co wuro intam kang dii kwama a yoceu yaken lam tureni bo kacek kange dikero gwam dor dikero kwama toki fiyaco nyi nob tokkaker dukumer wucakeu.
\v 22 Musa tok bilenker yiki Tee kwama an kunkumen kange nii ker dukumer na mo mor kebkumebo. kam nuwa dike cayikomtiyeu gwam.
\v 23 An yilam niwo nuwabo nii ker dukumer wurori ciiyan tungumco ciko win nubo locem
\v 24 Nyo nob ker dukumebo terti dor samailar kange burom bou bwiko cekeu cin tokker ciin cwungkang kumetinimbo wuro.
\v 25 Kom bibei nob kerdukumerowo kange noroceu wo cima kange Tengwanub kumubeu, kambo ciyi Ibrahim mor tueluwe dor bitiner gwam ciyan fiya bibwiyer.
\v 26 kambo kwama kun nyum bwe tomange ceri ci ter tomangekaco kumen wori nekom bibwiyer kambo yilam kikom fiya maka bwirankerer.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Kambo Btrus kange Yuwanna cin yi nubo kero tiyeu nii wabeu kange, nii durko kuwabeu, kange Sadukiyawa cin bou dor cer.
\v 2 kwomci bichom wori Bitrus kange Yuwana merang nubo nenti dor Yesu, la ci ne fulen kwenka cekoti buwareu.
\v 3 La cin tam ci cin kuken ci lo kuka na finin celum. wori men dom.
\v 4 La nubo buro nuwa tomange ciyeu cin ne bilenker kilaka nubeko nabarobbo bikate nung wuro ne bilenkere.
\v 5 Celfini ceri nubo tam ki ciyeu kange nubo durko kange nob merangkab cin mwerkangi wurcalima.
\v 6 Ana nii wabe durko wi wi, kange kayafas, kange Yuwana, kange Alexanderi, kange nob naniya nii wabeko durko.
\v 7 Kambo ci bou ki Bitrus kange Yuwana tiber cer la ci me ci ki bi kwando wini kaka dendo wini ka mam woticike?
\v 8 La Bitrus dim ki yuwa tangbe kwama yi ci, “Kom ko tam ki nobeu kange nubo dur nubero.
\v 9 Na nyo duwen kom ki me nyo ker nagenero kendo ma niwo nuwa bo lumanineu-Lama nyi nii wo yilam kwamere?
\v 10 la kom kange nubo Israila la wuro a yilam nyam nyome kimen wo nii wo tim fou ka kom kwamer mor dene Yesu Kiriti wo nazaret deu, wo ka kulkenceu, la kwama kungum co bwar.
\v 11 Yesu kiriti cou tero wo culang kuwekeu wo kom nob mukabo ka koweu la co yilam tero culang kuweke.
\v 12 Fuloka mani nii kange nen wori dendo kange mani dimer di Kwama wo ci ne niffire na fiya fuloka kercere.”
\v 13 Kambo ci to bikwan nerer Bitrus kange Yuwana ri cin nyumom fuwai nube koni ma bo kiye ka. La citi nyumangi la cin nyumom Bitrus kange Yuwana cin yii wi kange Yesu.
\v 14 La cin to nii wo ci twabeu tim kange ci, la ci fue ki diker tokkar.
\v 15 La kambo ciyi nob tomange a dubangum fiye yime nub dirlorembedi. La ci tokkangi bwiti ci.
\v 16 Ba ma nubo buro nyi? kwaka nerer man, nangen nyumankar mani kang chek. La nyumom nyume nubo yim wurcalima nin gwam. La be man kibi kwan do ba kanagum tiye.
\v 17 La kati ta ca kaba ti ki wakako mor nobe labo yi cikero ki nyial, ci a tokre ker kange nii dor denerowo.
\v 18 La cin co Pita kange Yuwana mor cin yi ci kero ki yial cia tokre ker kaka merangka gwam kiden Yesur.
\v 19 La Bitrus kange Yuwana yici keno dong dong nuwe kwama na nyo bwnangten kom la'a kwamari, kom warkero.
\v 20 Mani nya dob tokka kerti dor dikero nya tomeu, kange wonya nuwameu.
\v 21 Bwiko ci yiten Bitrus kange Yuwana kero ki nyialri, la cin dob ci cin cu'u. Lafiya bo nure wo ci a tam citi ki kang keu. wori nubo gwam duktang kwama ti ki dikewo bwiyeu.
\v 22 Nii wo ki nyumka dukumero wo ki fulokau, chor cero kwini naar.
\v 23 kambo ci nyamkan cineneri, Bitrus kange Yuwana bou nubo lo cinin la ci yii ci dike liya nob wabebo kange nubo durko yi ciyeu gwam.
\v 24 La cin nuwa ri cin kung dir ciyero wari kwama nen cin toki “Teluwe” mo wo mo ma dii kwama moma dor bitinereu, kange caji kange dike more ceu.
\v 25 Mon tok kero ki yuwa tangbek nyi canga mwe tee nye Dauda, yebwi nubo yim kumtacile? fwingan ti nye la nubo ki kwa kan dikero bwir.
\v 26 Mon yiki “Liyabbo dor bitinereu mwer kangum dor cer wari la nubo dur cero mwerum na ci ma kiye kange Teluwe”.
\v 27 Bichom Hiridus kange Pontius Bilatus kange kumta cileyeu kange nubo Israila cin mwerkangi fo mor cinan lor na cin kwobkangi kange canga mweu wucakeu Yesu, wo corten nuwageu.
\v 28 Cin mwerkangum wari nacin mam dike kang mweko kange namweko amatiye.
\v 29 Na weu mo teluwe to kercero ki nyial ne cangab mwebo bi kwan tokka kerek mweko.
\v 30 Ta'aru kang mweko na twam la na ne diker yiromer kange diker nyumangkar a mani ki den canga mwe wucakkeu Yesu.
\v 31 Kambo ci dim kwob ka dilokeri, fiye ci mwerum wiyeu muka, cin dim ki yuwa tangbe kwamak cin tok ker kwamaro ki bikwan.
\v 32 Nubo ducce ne bilekereu dor ciro mwerum mwere. la kange nii yi bo ki diker cer na ce la nyeu dike na ciyeu win.
\v 33 Ki bikwan nob tomangebo ma kwaka diyek warkerer ciyero dor kwenka teluwe “bwareu, luma ko dur wo dorciyere.
\v 34 Nii kange mani wo fiyabo dikere wo ci buni kange dikere. wori nubo ki tang kini kange loni miyerangum la bou ki kyemer dikero wo ci miyeu.
\v 35 La cin yotina nob tomangeu nen, la kabkang nubo nen gwam dong dong kange dike ci cwiyeu.
\v 36 Yusufu wo nob tomangeb coti Barsaba (bwe bika nerek) Balewi nii Kubrus.
\v 37 Miyem take wo na ceu la bou ki kyemero yoti na'a nob tomange nen.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 La nii kange wi Anatiya wice safiratu, cin miyem take ciyeu.
\v 2 ananiya yurangum kangem wi mor kyemer takero (La kin nyom ka wicek) La ci bou ki tangnim kyemembo kabum nob tomangebo nen.
\v 3 La bitrus yi ki “Ananiya ye bwi mwa dob bwekelkele dou ner mwere na cer yuwa tangbek kwama nen cuerke na tam tangim kyemer takero.
\v 4 Na miyebeu, kebo na mwe, la miyemmeu bikwankero kebo na mweka? we nii coo dokti nangen do wo mor neere mweu? mwa cuerbo nob nen cuerke mwa cuerum ki kwama.
\v 5 Ki nuwa ka kere kowo Ananiya yari la bwiyam, la taito dur tam nubo wo nuwau gwam.
\v 6 Bibweyile kange bou tum co chom cinen bwiceu ki lalang ya cin furum cho.
\v 7 Kambo kang kenero ta'areri wicen dou nyombo dike yaken tiyeu.
\v 8 La Bitrus yii co “yii ye kenoka miye takeu nan nyo cen”. La chon toki ong na nyo ce”.
\v 9 La Bitrus yii cho, la manyi ka ciyam wari na kom cuwa yuwa tangbek Teluwe? To nani nubek kowo ya fuer bwemeu wo nyilo la na tuken nen kale.
\v 10 Danjang chon yar ti na cek chon bwiyam. Kambo bibei bayilobeu douweri bocifiya chon bwiyam, la cin tu cho ci cerken ciko kale cifuerti cho cunga bwece ko nen.
\v 11 Taito dur bou kuu kwama nen kange dor nubero gwam wo nuwa dike wo gwameu.
\v 12 nangen yiromer kange diker nyumankaro ducce matiye mor nobe kange nob tomangek ci mwer kangum gwam bentilen colomoner.
\v 13 La kangem mani ki bikwan neerer do wo a mwer dorti kange ciye. La cin wi ki bwiyale foh ducce kabum nubem.
\v 14 La nyeu, nubo buro ne bilenker yuktenti Teluwe nen, nubo kila-kila na barub kange natub.
\v 15 La ci turang nubo nuwabo lumau, ci yaken cike kong nure ci yokenci dor kwangnir, kangembo biciri, worina Bitrus cuu tiri, wuloceu cuuti dor kangem.
\v 16 Nubo ducce borangum ti ci nan lor kentangum wursalima la ci bou tiki nubo nuwa bo lumau, kange buro kelkelibo kwomci tiyeu. lan twam ci gwam.
\v 17 La nii wabe durko kwenu kange nubo wari kange ceu (nubo bwangten Sadukiyawa tiyeu) cin dimki kor ducce.
\v 18 Cin tabang nob tomangeu cin kuranken ci lo kuka.
\v 19 Mor kumeu bwe tomange kwama wucakeu bou wumom nyiloni lo kukako. La cho kuci kale, lan toki.
\v 20 Kom ya koti kabum nyilom ku wabe koyi nubo ker dumerowo.
\v 21 kambo ci nuwa weri la cin cuu kuh wabe ki celka finik cima merangkati, la nii wabe durko kange nubo loceu cin bou bo cin cho yim kange nob dir loreb, kange nubo dur nubero Israilau, cin tuken ci fiye kuka
\v 22 La nob nangebbo ya lo kuka konen ci fiyabo nii.
\v 23 nyon fiya lo kukako nungum nunge, nob chorkabo tirangum nyilok la wumi ri nya fiyabo nii mor,
\v 24 La nii dukro kuh wabeu kange nob wabebo durko nuwa ketito weu, la ner cero kwenum cin nyombo dike a bangum bwiko tiyeu. La ciki ye ba matiye.
\v 25 La kange bou yici nubo buro ka kumeu tirangum kuh wabe merang nubo nenti.
\v 26 La nii dur ko kuwabeu ya kange nob nangeneb ceu yan bou ki ci. Kebo ki kwobkanka kati yilo nubo mobangci.
\v 27 Kambo ci bou ki ciyeu cin nung ci kabum nob dir loreb, la nii wabe durko me ci ker.
\v 28 Yii ci “Nya yi kombo ki kibikwan tak kom mare merangka mor denewo? la wo kom dim mor wursalima ki merangka kumek La kom doti na ko yo buyalenii wo na yiram dornyer”.
\v 29 La Bitrus kange tangnim nob tomangebo toki tam nyo ne kwama dur kebo nob.
\v 30 Kwama teb nyebeu kung Yesu woro ka tualumeu ka kulken dor bwatiyer.
\v 31 Kwama duktangka cho kange catiyere ce na yilam liya kange nii cerka na ne Israila yiloka kange tabkan bwirang kerer.
\v 32 Nyeu nyon nob warkeb dike bwirangeu nyo yuwa tangbek kwama ko wo kwama ne nubo wo bwanten tiyeu, gwam.
\v 33 Kambo nob dir lorebo nuwa we di nerciron kayam ki bichom, la cin do na ci twalangum bibei tomangeu.
\v 34 La bafarice kange wi dendo Gamaniel nii merangka werfumer, wo nubo gwam necho durtiye, la chon kweni tok kero ki nyial a chokken bibei tomange kale biduwar bwiri.
\v 35 La chon yici kom nubo Israila ko to yora ki di keko cuiti na ko ma nubo buro neneu.
\v 36 ki kumeni wo Theudas kweni tii tu dorcero na kange diker nubo kwini kwob naar bwang cinenten la ci twalumchori nubo bwang cenententiyeu gwam cin yilam kange nii nuwa bo fulen ciyaer wi tak.
\v 37 Na chori kange nii Galilee dendo Yahuda wo ki kumeni kiyeka bou bolang nubo ducce, cho keneu kayam nubo buro bwang cinen tentiyeu yilam.
\v 38 Na wo ma yi komti ko dubang nubo buro, ko dob ciki kwaciye, na no yukan ciyero kange nangen ciyero na nubo ciyeri an kayam.
\v 39 La na dike wuro na kwama ceri mani ka kangti kati yilo yilam ko ma kiye ti kange kwama. La cin ciya.
\v 40 La cin cho nob tomangeu mor la ci buk ci la yici kero ki nyial a tok re ker ki den Yesu.
\v 41 La cin cerum kabum nob dir lorembonen ci ti bilangi wori cin daten ci nuwa dotange ki ker denero.
\v 42 Bwiko nyeu citi yai kur waber kir-kir. Ci bwang ten ti luwe ci ne fulen ker kwamaro ti, La ci ma merangka ti ci kurong bowi citokti Yesu Cho Kritti.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 mor kumeniwo kilaka bibei tomange yoktenti la yafudawa yim biten Elenawa cin ter fuenna dor Yafudawa Israila wori ci cuwa bo tu kange natub buneb cibo, fiye kabkanka carik kabkangti kir-kireu.
\v 2 Kwob chilombo yobeu cho bibei tomangeu kila kila cinen la yici yorbo dubom nangen kwamar na yila kabkanka carik.
\v 3 La nyeu ko chok nubo niber na barubbo more kume, nubo ki ciniyeu din kiyuwa tangbe, kange nyonka, buro ba yotenti dor nangenero weu.
\v 4 ka nyeu, kwobka dilo kange tokka kerek ceko kir-kir.
\v 5 Ker chiyero lom nubo nen gwam, la ci chok Istifanus nii dim ki bilenkere, kange yuwa tangbe kwamak, kange Filibus, kange Prochorus, kange Nicanor, kange Timon, kange Parmenas, kange Nicolaus nii Antakiya wo ma yiloka Yahudanci yeu.
\v 6 Nubo ne bilenkereu bou ki nubo buro kabum nob tomangeb, la kwob cinen dilo ci yo cinen
\v 7 La ke kwamaro yoten kang ti wai, la kilaka bibei tomangeu wursalima yokten ducce, la nob wabebo ducce yilam nob neka duwek fiye bilenkero wiyeu.
\v 8 La Istifanus dim ki luma kange bikwan ma diker nyumankar ti kange diker yiromer mor nobe.
\v 9 La kangen nob kweni wo na bi kur wabero ce, choti bi kur waber cerka, wo kuramiyawa kange Iskandariyawa, kange biten kili kiya, kange Asiya. Nubo buro kwob kangi kange Istifanus,
\v 10 La cin mani kibi kwan ker nyomkar kange yuwa tangbe ko Istifanus tokkero ti cikeu.
\v 11 La yurangum yurange ci bol nubo ya a tok ki, Nyo nuwa Istifanus tok keti dila kati dor Musa kange kwama.
\v 12 Cin bol nubo durko kange nob mulankabor, lan cin lam bidom kange Istifanus cintam cho, cin bou ki cho kabum nob dirlorem.
\v 13 Chin borangu ki nob warker cuiker, wo toke, nii wo dobbo tokka kereko bwir dor fiye wucakkewo, kange werfuner.
\v 14 La nyon nuwa chon toki Yesu wo najaret reu an wurongum fiye wo na fulongum dam Musam bo dob bineneu.
\v 15 Nubo gwam yim dir loro neneu yo cinenten nuwe ciyero La chin toh tikob cebou na tikob bibei tomange wucakkeu.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Kambo nii wabe dur tokki mi digenwuri na ken bicom ka?
\v 2 Stephen toki yimi kange Teemi, kom nuwaye. Dukum kwamaro wo kange Abraham ki kwama me sopotamia, na nyimde ciyi firen Haran.
\v 3 Ci nyico ki, dubom bitine mwe kange tengwanim mwembo na yaken biti wuro ma nungmeven tiye.
\v 4 Dila chon dubom biten chaidean la yim mwor Haran, di wiri bwiyaka tee cekkori kwama bou ki cho mwor takke wo, fiye mu yimwi naweu.
\v 5 Chon necho kangem nob wuro wari kange ce na Tikange cho. mani bi duware ce, bwen wo mwa fuwam natiye dor cere, la chon tum fou ner bwentano Abraham manki bweri kon matin necho takke wo ca nyimtiye gwam kange ten gwanim cero bwan tano con bwiyam di
\v 6 kwama yico kerti na wuro nubo loca ciya yi bidom bitine nubo kange. Nyo fiyeyinu cho limbo dige bwiye atin bou chinen ki yera na bibei canga catin nuwa dotange na choro kwini kwob naar.
\v 7 La man ma bolang kale kowo neci dotange tiye kwama ki ciya cheruw nacin wab ye fiye wo nen.
\v 8 La kwama ne Abraham diker wabka, di la Abraham yi lam tee Ishaku lan wabum cho ki. kume narube, Ishaku yilam Tee, la Jacob yilam tee bibei yo wab culom bo yobe
\v 9 Kambo yitub cebu ciyabo kange Joseph la cin miyem cho nab yamembo Egypt La kwama kange cho.
\v 10 La cercho mor dotange cenen. La neeh Joseph fofka kange yomka kabum Pharaoh liya Egypt wo yocho dur nubero gwam mor Egypt kange mor lowenen gwam.
\v 11 Kambo ci ma wura dure di titen macar kange kan ana kange dotange durko tebbebbo nuwa la ci fiyabo cari.
\v 12 La Jacob wo nuwa carito wini masar di cho ci tom tomange ciya bou ki bwo kabo.
\v 13 kambo chiya boka na yobe ceri, la Yusufu fweltang keb cebonen dor cer ki kwa curo fir auna nyimom yitub Yusufu.
\v 14 Yusufu yi yitub cebo chiya bou ki tee che Yakubu kange diker ciyero kange bibei yo locheu firen Masar, gwam ciye nubo cibi kwini niber culombou nung.
\v 15 Yakubu choken yim firen biten Masar la chon bwiyam kange Tee ce.
\v 16 Chin tucho mor Shechem la chin yoken cho mor tuwi wo Abraham Teni ki kyemer bibwe Hamor nen Shechem.
\v 17 La ki kwama bi bwiyer kwamaro bidomeri Kwama yi Abraham nubo an duwi mor Egypt be.
\v 18 La chin yoh kange liya wi Masar wuro yumbo Yakubu.
\v 19 Liya chiro bol nubo ne tebyebbo dotange kambou ken chin dukchi tebyebo ki ciya cukou dor cero fiye dotange mani ciya dobchiti.
\v 20 Ki kwama wo chi bou Musa, Cho yori kabo nanimde kwama na yocho chuwakko taar mor loh tee ce.
\v 21 kambo chi yoken cho kaleri bwebubya Pharaoh's tumcho kung cho na yilam bibwe che.
\v 22 Musa wiki yulang merang biten Egypt kange bikwan keret kange nangen.
\v 23 kambo cho dou choroti kwini naar re ri chin kwabi mor nere ce ki cha tou yice bibei Israila.
\v 24 La chon to nii kange ti Musa tikaan niwa ci nuwa dotange ki twalka bama care.
\v 25 Kwaneri Musa na ci ciya takali kwama bou cinenne di la mani nyo. Chin yombo Kwamaki kancak cha chok chi la chi yombo.
\v 26 Chelfini chin bou irsailawa kangumbo ki kwalkangi bwiti chi la chin mani nacho bouchinen ki filang bwiti yichi ki yebwi kom kwerkanti bwitikume?
\v 27 Dila nii wo ter keceu tuken cho firen yi ki necho liyar do wo more che?
\v 28 Muki cwi muki namun twalum yoh kambo mwa twalum Israilawa wure ka?
\v 29 Musa chawaken kambo cha nuwa wori chon yilachinendiker yumankar biten Midian, wo cha yilam Tee bibeiyo yobou.
\v 30 Kambo choro kwini naare chum meri bibei tomange cher cenen mor Yeri bang sinai ki biyen kiret mor yere.
\v 31 Kambo Musa toh kirak keri yimanka lan fiyacho, lan chi kutau ten bidom na chi toh yora, chin nuwa dir kwama tok ti ki, Mo mi kwama tee mwe, Ibrahim kange Ishaku, kange Yakubu, kange Masu cwam tai fwe ki kungka dor nacir to.
\v 32 kwama yi cho ki chukom tai mweu fiyemin tim wiyeu. liyar kwama.
\v 33 Kwama yi cho ki chukom taa mweu namwek fiye mun tim wiyeu nku wabe.
\v 34 Kebo koni nubo lomi nuwa dotangeti masar la min nuwa fubom ciyembo, no nyori manya na chukom chi sanakowo, bou na twom nen Masar.
\v 35 wuro cho Musa chi kuwe dila kom ki we doknen ni warka dor nyere cho niwo kwama tomou na yilam ni dure kange ni cerka kwama ni bwirer kambo cho tou mor kiye.
\v 36 Musa yaki chi mor masar kambo cha madukum mor chachi ki kume kwini naar.
\v 37 Musa yi nubo Israilawa ki kwaka an yoh kumen nyi wabe dur bitine kume, yotob kumeb na mou.
\v 38 Won cho nii wo wari kange nobe mwor kiye ki no tob kange nob dukkumen wuro bwangten ka cho chi mane tokkang ker dor ter Sinail cho wo wari kange teb yebbo wuro cho ni wuro ne nyo ker kwama.
\v 39 Won cho niwuro tebyebbo ko neka ko bidwiyere ci chikom cho more ciye, chin ne birum neri chiki yang masar.
\v 40 Ki kwama chi tokti ki Aruna na ywel chimen kwama wo a yati ki chi mor masar reu. diker Musa ro churou firen masare nya nyombo diker bwikange ceu.
\v 41 La chin ywel be kwame chi bo bi bwitin chukko na ywel kako koce, chin bilangi diker chi mani ki kang chekeu.
\v 42 Kwama kangum chi la chin ya bilang bitenrendo diye kambo mu langum bifumer nob duktanka kom neye twimen kundo fichangeu. firen ki choro kwini naar wuro kom Israilawa?
\v 43 Kom ciya kange kwama Molech kange kwama biteiren wo Rephan, kange wolo kom yulange. na kom wabci, man yi kikom firen kah Babila ki den canga.
\v 44 Tuka kume kibi kur fulen firen ki na nungi chin wi. kambo kwama ma nagen ki Musa ki cha mani na wuro chi nung chineneu.
\v 45 Wo cho bikur fulendo tuka kume bou chike ki kwama Joshua wuro bou ki kwama chi yo bitine kange wo nubo kange ce wo kwama ywachiye wi kabum tuka kume nen na choro nyo yaken ki kwama Dauda.
\v 46 Wo fiya bilangka kwama nen diker bwiyeu chin ywel ku wabka kwama ki kwama yakubu ce.
\v 47 La Suleimanu ywel ku kwama.
\v 48 Di la nii liyare mani yi fiye nubo yulangi ki kange na wuro nii dukkome tokke.
\v 49 Di kwama na liyar ce kalewuro ceu na yoka nanice di la luwe wini ka mumentiye? kwama toki nyowe, kakka fiye wuni wo ma fubomtiye?
\v 50 Kebo nuremi kom manag diwura?
\v 51 kom nubo ki kwichi duweu, wo nero biyebe kange wuro tuni mani nuware, nachuro nyo kom cwibo bibwiyer bifumero kom mati dike tuka kume mane.
\v 52 Nob dukkomen wuni tuka kume nebo dotange chin twalangum nob dukommeb wuro baurangu ki kabawuro ki liayre kom yilam nob kange ceb kange nubo twalang chiye.
\v 53 Kom nob mulang kako, kom yuwou bolange wo nob bi bwiyeror bouchike di kom mabo nangen chiko.
\v 54 Kambo bibei tomange nuwa nyori nar chero kayam kambo ken, di chin ku mum chiyero ti chi ciyabo ki Istifanus.
\v 55 Di la Chi dim ki yuwa tangbek chin kung nuwe ce di kwama, chin duktang kwama mati chin taou kiriti timye kango catiyet wo kwama ce.
\v 56 Istifanus toki to mitodi kwama wumom, fou bibwe nifirenen tim tiye foh kang ko chatiyer kwama ce.
\v 57 La nob tareu chin kungi chin kwa diro kibi kwan, la chin kumo tuniciye chu ki keciye win chin kwencinenten.
\v 58 Chin chukom cinar lower choci mubang ce ki ter, na nung dike bwiye, la chin cikangum bellen cero durko chi yoti kabum bwe kange chi chuwoti ki Sawulu
\v 59 Ki kwama mubang Istifanus cho yila chuwoti chi tokti teluwe me Kiriti yo bibwiyer miro.
\v 60 Chon chungi chon kwa diro kibi kwan choki Tee me kwama tare bwirang kero dor cher kambbo toki nyeri la chin damdum.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Bulus ciya kange buwero. Kikwamacho dotange chilendo kwenu dor nob kwama miro wursalima, di la nubo nebilenkertiyeu ciin yalam gwamm mor bitine Yahudiya kange samariya, cii dob ka nob tomangeb.
\v 2 Nabarubbo kibilenke chin furum Stephen laciyi yim kang buwam dorcer.
\v 3 Di la Sawulu ma nob kwamabo nen diker kambo ken chiti doi luwe-luwe chi cikangum nabarobboti kange natubo, kumcitak furcina.
\v 4 Duwa nubo neken bilenke birombo yalamem, chinen ya chine ker kwamaro.
\v 5 Filibus yaken firen Samariya toker Yesuroti.
\v 6 Kambo nubo nuwa lacitoten dikero Filibus matiyeri, lachin yilaken ki ner chero gwam na nuwau dike chitoktiyeu.
\v 7 Won kelkeliyo bwirko chiranyu bwinubo ducce no nuweceu chin ciwiyeti kidir nubowo kwamang be kange kilentinimbo fiya twaka.
\v 8 La chin ma fuwor nerer ducce bitinecho.
\v 9 Nii kange wi bitinecho choti ki Siman. wo kikabe chin nikuye latakri chima nubo Samariyamin diker nyimanti nawo chi cho dorceriti ki chin diro kange.
\v 10 Kwrub Samariya nubo dur kange bibei nuwa choti cikinyi ki “Niwo cho bikwan duret kwamaro wocii choti ki dureu.
\v 11 Chi nuwa choti wori kutangnyi machinen diker nyimankati ki kwomje- kwomjece.
\v 12 La kambo chi ne bilenke kange ker waber Filibus ceri, wo chi mati ker liya kwama kiden Yesu kriti lachin yuchinen mwem kwamambo gwamce nabarub kange natub.
\v 13 Cho siman kibwicho ne bilenke kambo ciyu cinen mwem kwamamberi la chin mwerkang kange Filibus kambo chito cii ma diker nyimanka ti kange nanyendo dureri, la kwomchoti.
\v 14 kambo nob tomangeb wursalima nuwa fulende samariyau yo kerkwamareri cii tuncinen Bitrus kange Yahaya.
\v 15 kacilauweri, ciin kwobcinen dilo naci yo yuwatangbe kwamako.
\v 16 Wori bwiri yuwatangbe kwamako yiraubo dorcher bwiri, chin yucinen ka mwem kwamambo kiden Tee kwama Yesu.
\v 17 La Bitrus kange Yahaya cin yo cinenten kanceu dorcer lachin yo yuwa tangbe kwama.
\v 18 Kambo siman to cii yuwatangbe kwama koti kiyeka kange nob tomangeb dorcerdi lanne chi kyemer.
\v 19 Yici, ki “kom neye bikwandowo ken, lawo niwo miyo yo cinenti kanko dorcerei na yo yuwatangbe kwamako.
\v 20 Di la Bitrus yicho ki, nawori mweu a yanchang kange mwo. wori muti kwain mwan fiya yuwatangbe kwamake ki chuweka mwek.
\v 21 Mu manki chuner fou dikero wuronen, wori mor nere mweu kebo dong-dong kwama nen.
\v 22 Nyori ywelum bwirang ker mwero, di la kwob dilo kwama nen kangeri an dob mwen bwirang ker mwero muyo ner mwereu.
\v 23 Wori min nyimom mumor kanka nerek tak ri, mor bwaka nerek.
\v 24 Siman ciya yiki “kwobka dilo kwama nen kermir, dike kange mor dikerwo mtokeu, a abwire kange mwo.
\v 25 Kambo Bitrus kange cidim ne kaker kwamareri, chin yilaken wursalima, ciyakenti dor nurer di, cin wab ker kwamaro chinar lor Samariya ducce.
\v 26 naweu bwe tomange kwama yi Filibus ker ki Kweri yaken chunyako bang nure yirau tob kange wursalima yaken Gaza (Nure wo ki no kwechane.
\v 27 Kweri yaken nikange wo ciro Abaca, in Liyar dur Chunya kandu katu, liya Abaca. cho cima liyar kulen choro tiye gwamme Bou wursalima cama wabkerwi.
\v 28 Yikenti yimyie diker yamercer kiye, bifumer Ishaya niker dukumer.
\v 29 Yuwatangbe ko yi Filibus ki “yaten bidom kange kulend kwikarowo”.
\v 30 Filibus cwa yanfiyacho nuwa ci kiye bifumer Ishaya ne ker dukkumerti la ciki mum nyimom dike me kiyetiyeu?”
\v 31 Bahabashe yiki “amanye manyumantiye caro kange fwetang membori? ken Filibus adou mor diker kwika ceronen nayi kange cho.
\v 32 Won cho dikero Bahabashe kiyeti “Ciin yaken kicho mu kwame fiye biyeka bir-bir tak na be kwame kom nob cangkab, wombo nyi.
\v 33 Dor yiber dorer cer ci macinen bolang kebo mor luma we ane kercero car kotiye? wor cii tum dukumece dorbitiner.
\v 34 La Tee me filibus yiki, “min kennen yiye we niker dukumerowo tok kero wotiye? kidor cer kaka'a nikange kidumenka?
\v 35 Filibus Teer kero dor bifumer Ishaya Lan ma cinen ker kwamaro.
\v 36 Kambo ciyaken nureri, cin lam kong caji kange Tee wuro yiki “To, mwambo wofo, yebwi mani a yumen mwem kwamam botiye?
\v 37 Filibus yiki “No mun ne bilenke win mor nerer mweri, cin yumwen mwem kwamambo. Dila Bahabashe yiki minne bileke.
\v 38 La Bahabashe yiki atim kidiker kwikaro. Lachin yuchinenmwembo.
\v 39 Kambo chi cherum mwembo nenneri yuwatangbe kwamako dum Filibus Teeu totensobo tak, la yakenti naken bilang tumboti.
\v 40 Dila filibus cerkangeu Azotus. Tiyangem bitinecho token ker kwamamaroti bitine cho nen yacin lamciko kaisariya.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Di la Shawulu yoti kantni tikanka kerek tayek kange twalangka nob bwangka Yesu chere ni wabe durkonen.
\v 2 Kentencho bifumer naci yaciko kuwabe kwamamu Dimaskus, wori no fiya ni nanure woceri Bwayile kange nawiye, naci bou kici wursalima naci bwamci.
\v 3 kambo liyakentiyeri chin dadom kange Dimaskus dang jang, dang jang filango yirau di kwama kangtangumcho.
\v 4 lachin yarken bitineri cin nuwa diro kange yichoti “Shawulu, Shawulu yebwi mu neye dotange tiye?
\v 5 Shawulu ciyi toki kii we mwo kwama?” kwama yicho “mo Yesu wuro mune dotange tiyeu.”
\v 6 Di la kweni doken mor cinar lorcho ciyam yinen dikerowa tamyo maneu.
\v 7 Nubowo yakenti kange shawulu tirangum bir-bir cin lem diker tok kar, chi nuwa dirti, dila citobo nii wii.
\v 8 Shawulu kweni bitine kambo chi wom nuwe ceri, mani ci toh dikerti, lacin tacinen kango cinbouki cho mor cinar lor Dimaskus.
\v 9 lam kume taar manici toti manici cati, manici noti.
\v 10 Nii tomange kange wi Dimaskus dencero Hannaniya, dila kwama tok ker kange cho mor dukumer yicho ki “Hannaniya” ciki To, minwo kwama”
\v 11 Kwama yicho, Kweni yaken cinarloro choti ki Mikakke, lo niwo choti ki Yahuza me ni bou Tarsus dencero Shawulu, ci kwob diloti.
\v 12 Chinto mo dukume nikange douti dendo Hannaniya wi douti dila kun kang yocinenti wori nuweceu na wumom.
\v 13 Di la Hannaniya ciya kwama min nuwa fulen nubowin ducce dor niwon kange dara bwiram nanye net cero cima nubo lomwennen wucakeu yim wursalima.
\v 14 Liya wabe durko necho nyal naci tam gwamm nubowo chodencerotiyeu.”
\v 15 Dila kwama yicho ya cho cin kulen nangenner minr min chokum cho choke wo awaden miroti nubo nenneu kange liyabtinib kange Israila.
\v 16 Wori man dancinen dotange ca nuwati ker denerer miu.”
\v 17 la Hannaniya yaken doken luwecho. yocinenti kanko dor, yiki “kemi shawulu Yesu toki wo dandorcer munen nure kikwama mu boutiyeu, toh muye nati fiya toka fiyek nadimki yuwa tangbeko wucakeu.
\v 18 dang jang dikero kange no wulom dikem nuwe shawulu, la fiyam toka fiyek kwene cin yucinen mwem kwamambo.
\v 19 La chamcharito cho ci necho bikwam neret yi wari kange nob bwangkab wi Dimaskus kumeni kila.
\v 20 Wi danjang neker Yesurti mor kuwabe yitki incho bibkwe kwama.
\v 21 kwarub nubo nuwa cho tiyeu cin yimangti ciki “wo kebo niwo twalang nubo wursalimatiya choden do wotiyeu ba? ciboufota natamci cineken liya wabe durko.”
\v 22 Di la shawulu fiyam bikwan kambo ken ci bouti ki kwamka kange bolka tiber Yafudawar kange nubo yim Dimaskus ki nurewo ci dancimen Yesu incho Kristi.
\v 23 Ki kumeni kila nawo chumeu, Yafudawa mwer kangi nacin twallum cho.
\v 24 Di la Nyomom dike mwertiyeu. Cii chirou choti nyilo kalek cinar lorocho nacin twallum cho.
\v 25 Di la ki cin kumeri nob bwankabo tuh cho mor bulene chin dokken cho tiyak.
\v 26 Kambo chi bou wursalimari, shawulu cwinaci mwerkandor kange nob bwangkab. Di la kwarub ce ci cwachoti wori ci ciyabo chokeneu cin yilam nii bwangkaba.
\v 27 La Barnabas tuh cho bouchiko nob tomangebo nen. yici kambo Shawulu wabkan kange kwama nureu. Di la kwama tok kero kange cho, shawulu ma tok ker Yesu nyang lang Dimaskus.
\v 28 Wabkanci kwama dotacek kange cerkacek wursalima. In tok ker kwamar nyanglang mor den Yesu.
\v 29 Chin ma kwobkanke kange Yafudawa Helenawa, dila cinti naci to chi twallumcho.
\v 30 Kambo kebbebo nyimom nyeri, cho ci beken kicho Kaisariya. ci tunkencho Tarsus.
\v 31 Lana nyime Ekilisiya gwam biten Yafudiya. Galili kange Samariya ci fiya luma kange muka lachi yi yim cimbo ti mor tai kwama, kange birim nerem Yuwatangbe kwamak, nob kwamabo kila chiko chob ten.
\v 32 Yilam kambo Bitrus buyelangum chunka bitinen kocho gwam, yilam nob bwanka kwamake yim biten Lydda.
\v 33 Cin fiya nii kange dendo Aeneas, wur bwiyo nom nowe, dim choro narub dor kwangnid.
\v 34 Birtus yicoki Aeneas, Yesu kiristi twamnen. kweni kun diker damer mwero. nawonyo kweninti.
\v 35 La gwamm nubo biten Lydda kange biten sarona cinto niiwo, dila cin yilau fiye kwama wiyeu.
\v 36 Naweu ni kwama kange wi yafe dendo tabita, dendo Kinug “Dorcas” Nawiye wo dimki mana nangen do ken cii bwini nubo manki dikereti.
\v 37 In lam kwama wo ci daken twira la cin buyam, kambo ci Yuchinen mwembo ci yokencho luwe diyeu.
\v 38 Dila Lydda bidom kange yafa nob bwanka be nuwa Bitrus kinon firen cin twom nubo yob cinen. Cii kenchoti, “Tabre bwi bou nyinen”.
\v 39 Bitrus kweni yaken kange ci, danjang ci bouri, cho ci yaken kicho luwe diye. La natub bunebo bouti ti bidom chiwiyeti, la chin tuh belendo kange kulendo Dorcas churcineneu ki kwama ciwariyeu.
\v 40 Bitrus cho kumai gwamm mor kuwe, chunken kwob dilo, dila yila chunya twarek, kii, “Tabita kwenuu”. ci wom nuweceu, cito Bitrus ri chin yiken.
\v 41 Bitrus tar kanceko kunnyu cho lana nyime chou bwanka kwamako kange natub bunebo, cin neci Tabita ki dume.
\v 42 Dikerowo yilam nubo nyimom gwamm yafa, la nyori nubo ducce ne bilenke kwama nen.
\v 43 La yilam Bitrus yi kumeni kila kange Yafa kange ni kange dendo saminu Majemi
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Nii kange nowi biten Kaisariya dendo karnilious cin dur nob kwenebo cii choti ki Istifanus.
\v 2 Inni wabe, wo neken dorcero kange loceu bwanka kwamak; ne tikali kemerti ducce Yafudawa nen kwob dilo fiye kwama wiyeu, kir-kir.
\v 3 Ki kang keneko taar na yimkakumbo ce cin bou cinen mor dukumer bwe tomange kwama bouti cinen dila bwetomange kwama toki ki, “Karnilious”.
\v 4 karnilous cin cii bwetomange kwama ninten nuwe mortaye. inye ni luwe?” Bwe tomange kwama yicho ki “dilo mweu luma nere mweko nune nubo bwinibotiyeu, lam di kwama nan luma nerer diker kwama kabum kwama.
\v 5 Naweu, twom nubo aya biten Joppa ciya bou ki nii chuwoti Saminu woci choti ki Bitrus ceu.
\v 6 Yim kange Saminu nitu tiye, wolocen kino kon chachi.
\v 7 kambo nii to mange wo tok kero ceu yilanken di, Karnilious Chuwo yob mor bibei changa loceu, kange nii kwene win mor tangne cenen wuro bwanten kwama tiyeu.
\v 8 Karnilious yici dikero bweuwe gwamm la twomei Jappa.
\v 9 Celfinice ki kan keneko nukkune (Kikakuk) ci yakenti kambo cidadom kange cinar loreri Bitrus kwiken luweu diyeu naci kwob dilo.
\v 10 La cin nuwa wura lacin cwiti diker cakarti, lakambo nubo macaritiyeu dila cin toh dukum.
\v 11 La cin toh dikwama wumom dila kangum cembo yirauti, kange diker na lalango dur yirauti dor bitiner, ci chorumti chunga ceko nareuniu.
\v 12 Morece biciro fwelfwele nako narreu gwamm wi kange nubo kongti kongeu, dorbitiner kange bilibe tinim dii kwama.
\v 13 Di la diro tok ker kange cho Kweni Bitrus, biyeucho.
\v 14 Di la Bitrus yike, kebongo kwama wori, micambo dike wucakke wi kange dike yeinyeu”.
\v 15 Di la diro bou chinen yobeceutak, “dike kwama mamco wucakkeri chore muki yeikabo.
\v 16 Wuro bwiu kinti taar, dila ciin tum kwelen yaken dii kwama.
\v 17 Kambo Bitrus mor kwomka ki danke dukumembo citoweri, dila nubo Karnilious twomou bou tiran gum nyilok locho, kambo ci mem nureri.
\v 18 Dila cin ma attifolo cimen nii chuwoti ki Saminu Bitrus ceu yiraufoka.
\v 19 Kambo Bitrus mor kwakakerek dor dukumer yuwa tangbe kwamako yicho ki “To, nubo yoh donenti.
\v 20 Kwani yirau yaken kange cii mare bwi yambo nenkange ciyeu wori mo mi twom che”.
\v 21 Bitrus yirau nubonen yice ki mo komdo tiya. yebwi kom bowe?
\v 22 Ki dur nub kwenebo ceroti ki karnilious niken wo bwangten kwamatiyeu, nubo Yafuda nyumom cho choniwo bwe tomange kwama wucakkeyeu twomuu na mu bou loche, nuwa tomange munen.
\v 23 La Bitrus chouci ciya dou mor naci yiken kange cho. celfiniceri yaken wari kange ci la kangem bo Yafa yoci nure.
\v 24 Celfiniceri cin doken kaisariya Karnilious ningtsng citi, chou kebcebo kange farub cebo bidomeu.
\v 25 kambo Bitrus doweri karnilious takange nuwe kange cho chungi necho dur.
\v 26 Di la Bitrus kuncho yichoti kweni ti mo keneu niffir.
\v 27 Ki kwama Bitrus tokkankerti kangeceu, doken mordi kwabti nubo ducce mwerum fiye win.
\v 28 Yi ciki “Komki bwikom kom nyimom nii Yafuda mani mma naniyak kaka'a na ya kange nen, kaka'a bitine kange. Dila kwama yiye ki chokeni manki wucakke.
\v 29 Wo dike bwi mabou nyimanka maniye, kikwama kacou Yereu. la yori minne yebwi kom twomi komkin bowe”.
\v 30 Karnilious yiki kumeni naar wo chumeu dong dong kwama wo, mi kwob diloti ki kwama Tee rou, (kang keno taareu) mor luwemi, mintori tinkani ki kulendo fuwor.
\v 31 Yiki Karnilious kwama nuwam dilomweu tikali mweu nubonen i nkwa kwamanen ki mwo.
\v 32 La nyori twomkange yafa, two min a chomwen nii kangewi dendo Saminu wo ci chotiki Bitrus. kiyi cho saminu ni chu tee tiyeu, yim kong caji.
\v 33 Na weu cin twom cinen cha bou gwam ce na cin mwerkange wi kabom chem kwama na chi nuwa dikero gwam wo cha yici ki ciya maneu ki dencer Teluwe.
\v 34 La Bitrus karcinen ki Biling ke miu nyimom kwama mani nuwo ki dimen.
\v 35 Lan nyori mor nubo gwamm niwo wab chotiyeu kange ni madiker yoryoreu kwama yochoti.
\v 36 kom nyimom tomange cinen Israila ki kwamawo ci yici kero lumer fiye Yesu Kristi wiyeu woncho kwama wucakakeu.
\v 37 Kom ki bwikom kom nyimom dikero birombo bwiuweu, wo bwiu mor Yafuda terti Galili kambo tomangeYukan munnyek kwama wo Yahaya maneu.
\v 38 Nannyeng tinim Yesu nii Nazaret kambo kwama yomcho ki yuwa tangbe ceko wucakkeu. kange bikwan duret. Dila yoti kanwi ma nangen lumarti kange twaka nubeko gwamm brombo bwe kelkele bwomeu, wori kwama kange cho.
\v 39 Nobu tom dikero camaneu gwamm biten Yafudawa kange mor wursalima wuro Yesu wo citwallume, kiyeika dor chilom bwatiyeu.
\v 40 Ni wuro kwama kungum cho kikume taare dila yilam nubo nyumom cho.
\v 41 Kebo nubonen kwarub, dila nubowo kwama choci ki kaba-biki bwibo nubo ba cha bano wari kannge cho kambo kwama kuncho mor tuweu.
\v 42 Yibo bi yi nubo ker kwamaro biyitenci wocho wuro kwama yo a ma dumeti kange bwar bolang tiyeu.
\v 43 Nob dukum kerem gwamm dokker cero, wuyak, birom ne bilinke tiyeri nafiyam cherka mor deneche.
\v 44 Kambo Bitrus tok keroti dor dikero biromberi, yuwa tanbge kwamako yirau dor kwarub nubo yirom wi nuwa ker kwama roti cinen.
\v 45 Nubo wuro mor mwerkangka nob bangka kwamakeu, cin ciya ki mwati ka lareko, kwarub nubo bou kange Bitrus ceu nuwa nyimanka wori yuwa tangbe kwamako yirau dor nuber.
\v 46 Wori cin nuwa nubo biro tok keroti ki nyini kange chicaklang kwamati. Dila Bitrus ciya.
\v 47 Kange wi wuro aywam nubowoti yuka mwem kwama keu nabeu?
\v 48 Lan toki a yucinen mwembo kiden Yesu Kristi Lacin kencho ayi wari kange ci na kumewo.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Nawo nob nangenbo kange kebcebo wo Yahudiya nuwa ki nobo kumtacele ciken cin yo ker kwamaro.
\v 2 La Bitrus bo Ursalima, boro mor nobo mwatum bwi nabarube torang choti.
\v 3 Mo mwerkan dor kange nobo biye bo bwi nabarube, mon cha chari kange ci.
\v 4 Bitrus teri fwetancinen keroti ki.
\v 5 maki kwob dilo mor cinan lor yafa man to dukum bulen do yiraw nyona yilang ko dur wo ci cuku kwama culangko nare yirau kabum mim.
\v 6 Man nyo cimenti nuwe wi, take man bulange durcer, man to bi yuwaro nako nwar na dorbitinero ce, biyuwaro bwirko, kange buro kongti konge, kange bilibetinim bo dii kwama.
\v 7 Min nuwa diro yiyeti kwemi, Bitrus biyem wom.
\v 8 Miki kebo nyo teluwe dike kange mani wo kebo na wucake ce kange wo yai nye do nyi miye.
\v 9 Diro ciya firen dii kwama, ki dike kwama chuwo ki wucakke, chuwo moki kebo wucakke.
\v 10 dike bwi Kiriti taar nimde tuh yilanken ciko kwama.
\v 11 Can nawo nobo, taar tirangum kabum luwem bo nyo more ceu, ci tom ci firen kaisariya fiye ma wuye.
\v 12 Yuwa tangbe ko yiye nyo ya ware kange ci, nungka demene men. kebbebo wuro nukken ciya wari kange mo la nyo doken lo nii cuwo.
\v 13 Yi nyo kambo cho to nii tomange kwama tim mor luwece, yiti ki twom nob taar Yafa, ya ciya cho Saminu wo cuwoti ki Bitrus.
\v 14 Chan yi kom tomange wo ka fiya fulokati mo kange lomwe.
\v 15 Man ter kiro kange ci, yuwa tangbeko yirau dor cer nawo yira bineneu ki kaba.
\v 16 La man bulangi kange ker Teluwe, nawo cho toke, “Bilenke Yuwanna ma Yuu nub nen mwemti ki kume a ma kumen ki yuwa tangbe.
\v 17 Tano kwama neci nyomka nawo ne beri, fiya bo ne bilenke fiye teluwe Yesu Almasihu, man we ma kobkanti kange kwama?
\v 18 Ci nuwe dike wo ri lan bwayum diker tokkaker dila cin duktan kwama cike nobo kumtaceleu kwama neci yiloka ko ciya fiya dume tiye.
\v 19 Buro yila, ki ker dotange bwanten bwiko bwar Istifanus, cin kwiya ya lam finikiya, kuburus, kange kuranne, ci ba Antakiya, dila cin tok ker fulener, yesu Yahudawa nen ki kwaci.
\v 20 Di la kangem ciyembo nob bo kuburus kange kuranne, kurane, ci, bo Antakiya ci tok ker kange Helenawa, cin yi ci fulenker Teluwe Yesu.
\v 21 Take bikwan Teluwe (Ubangiji) wari kange ci, nobo dutce ne bilenker, cin yilau Teluwe nen.
\v 22 Fulen ciyero lam tii nob kwama bo Ursalima so ci tung Barnabas nob kwamabo, cin merang nobo dutce. Wi Antakiya ci ter cho ka nob tomangebo kritta.
\v 23 Di cho lau con to luma kwama co ma fuwor neret, chon nece bikwan gwam, ciya tim mor Teluwe, ki nerciyero gwam.
\v 24 Wuri chon niken dim ki yuwa tangbe kange bilenke, nobo kila cin yokten Teluwe nen.
\v 25 Barnabas cu Tarsus na cho do Shawulu.
\v 26 Fiyacho, chola bou ki cho Antakiya. cho yi wi Antakiya choro win ci mwerkanti kange nob kwama bo, cin merang nobo dutce. Wi Antakiya ci ter cho ka nob tomangebo Krista.
\v 27 Mor Kumeni rowo kangem nob nuwa ka dukume, bo Antakiya.
\v 28 Win more ciye dencero Agabus Kwini titiye tok ker ki bi kwan yuwa tange ki, an ma tik ka kanga kambo ken dor bitinero nin gwam. Wuro biwi kal Kalaudiya.
\v 29 La nob tomagebo tuki kor neret, wo ni ki ma nyi bi kwane ce, cin tun kebciyebo nin feren yahudiya ki tikali.
\v 30 Cin mani nyo, cin tung nobo durko nin ki kyemer, do kan Barnabas kange Shawulu.
\c 12
\p 
\v 1 ki kwama wo Hiridus dok kangem nob bwankabo nin kan na co nuwa cinen.
\v 2 Chon twallum Yakubu kange Yuwana ki kulen.
\v 3 Bwiko cho to nyo, lom yahudawa nin con ta Bitrus.
\v 4 Bwiko cho ta bitrus di chon kum cho Furcuna, chon yoti nobo tee kwentiyeu na a to co ti chon wii ner boka ki cho dukume yabka.
\v 5 La Bitrus kumkume furcuna, kange num kebcebo bwang ten kwamatiye kwob dilo ti kwama nen dor cer.
\v 6 nyo na fini Hiridus a chok cho fiye, mor kume wo, Bitrus dadumti tiber nobo te kwentiye yob, bwambwambe ki gwelmar yab, nob te kwentiyeu tirangum nyilo furcuna.
\v 7 Nyomka man di la ka nob tomange kwama wucakke cerkangu cinen filan ko tiba kuwe cho, ke Bitrus cungakin kuncho tak ki, Kweni wulom' di la gwelmaro kan ceke cherum.
\v 8 Ni tomange kwama wucakke yi cho ki, cakkangum kulen mwero dum tameu, Bitrus mani nyo yeyum yilam mweko, bwan men ten.
\v 9 Bitrus bwanten nii tomange wucakke, cin cerken kale, nyom bo dike nii tomange wucakke matiye, bilenke, ce ki ke dukum.
\v 10 Di la cin cum nobo to yiloko wine kange yobe, cin lam yiloko ci ma kyemere, wo to cinanloro tiye; wum cinen ki bwici, cin cerum, ci bwangten nure, wi dangjang nii tomange wucakke dobomcho.
\v 11 Bitrus yilau mor bwiyece, yiki bilenke man nyom naweu teluwe, tungu nii tomange ce wucakke bo na cok ye kan Hiridus kange dike yahudawa kwatiye.
\v 12 Cho nyomom yori, cho bou la Maryamu wo bou Yahaya, den Teecero Markus wobo bwanten Yesu tiye mwerkange wi dutce ci kwob dilo ti.
\v 13 Di chon kwa yiloko luweko la bubiya mor luwe chou bo na wom yiloko.
\v 14 Chon nuwa dir Bitrus bubiya ka timi bilangtum dolbo womka, yila cwa chu kuh na cho ne ci fulen Bitrus tim nyilo.
\v 15 Cin cho ki mo twelum twele, bubiya cinti, ki nyo. cike nii tomange ce wucakke ka.
\v 16 Bitrus titen kwaka yiloko la cin wom nyilokori, ci ton cho la dike nyomankar tamci.
\v 17 Bitrus nung ciki kang maci nenti ki ciya kumom. cho ci yi ci fulendo kambo teluwe cokce furcuna. coki kom yi Yakub kange kebbcebbo gwam. dike bwiye. cho dob ciye, chu fiye kange.
\v 18 Fini celi, kebo be kwalkanka kweni tiber nobo tekwentiye di bwi kange Bitrus.
\v 19 Bwiko Hiridus do cho fiya cho bo la chon me nobo totiye chon neci nyaldo a twallum ci, la cho yirau yahudiya yaken kaisariya, yi yim cem wi.
\v 20 Naweu Hiridus mam funer kange nobo Taya kange Sidon, cin chu fiye cho wiye wari, cinken Bilatus, ni tikali liya, a tikanci, dila cindo ywelka, wori ciki fiya carito bitine ce.
\v 21 bi diye wo ci yomom Hiridus cakkangum ki kulen liyare take yiken dor kuttile liyare, chon ma yiranci ker.
\v 22 Nobo kwa kiyange, ki wo dir kwamar, kebo na nifiroce.
\v 23 Wi dangcang nii tomange kwama wucakke kwa cho, wuri co ne bo kwama duktangka wi dangcang na yuwe cam co chon bwiyam.
\v 24 Ker kwamaro, ti kuyai yoktenti.
\v 25 Bwiko Barnabas kange Shawulu dim nagen ciyero Ursalima, ci yilauti, ci bo wari, kan Yahaya, woro din te cero markus (Barnabas kange Shawulu) cin yilaken Ursalima.
\c 13
\p 
\v 1 mor nob bwanka kwamanko Antakiya nob nuwaka dukumebo wi, kange nob merangka. ci bi Barnabas, Saminu woro ci (chuti ki Baki) kange lukiya Bakurane kange manayin woro ci (yo ci wari kange Liya Hiridus ni ca liyare) kange Shawulu.
\v 2 Di la ci wab kwamati ki yim bo ngak-ngak kange dulomwe, di yuwa tangbeko ki kom cok men Barnabas kange Shawulu dor nangen do ma cu ciye.
\v 3 Merka kwob dilo kange ngak-ngak kange dulomwe la ci yo cimenti kanko dur, ci yoci.
\v 4 Shawulu kange Barnabas cin bwanten dir yuwa tangbeko wucakke cincu culukiya, wuri cin yabken diyele kuburus.
\v 5 Fiya ci cinanlor salomi cin merang ker kwamaro mor kur bi waber Yahudawa, ci wari kange Yahaya Markus ni tikanci tiye.
\v 6 Bwiko cho chi kentangum diyele gwam, yaken Bafusa, foh ci fiya kange bayahudiya dencero Bar Yesu. nima fulentiye take nii nuwaka dukume cwerke.
\v 7 Ni fulene wo ci cuwo ti ki Makaddas, cho carju Bulus nii wo ki yilen ne. wuro cuwo co Bulus kange Barnabas co cwiti na cho nuwa ker kwama.
\v 8 Di la elima ne fulen (Fwetanka dene ce) kwabkangi kange ci cwiti na co fwem makadda cin bilenke nen.
\v 9 la Shawulu wo ci cho ti ki Bulus dimki yuwa tangbeko wucakke la yo cimen ten nuwe.
\v 10 La chon yiki mo bi bwe bwekelkele mo dimki bibolero kange cil. mo nii kiye dike ken. mani mwa dob werkanka nor Teluwe kwama tim cere tiya? naweu.
\v 11 kang teluwe kwama wo dor mwer, naweu yilam fukma. mani mo to kakuk ti can can do wo. Wi danjang ka bikumta kume kange kumtacele cumom cho chon ter bwelankako do nobo a ti cimen kang ko tiye.
\v 12 Bwiko Makaddaci to dike bwiri neken bilenke wurico ma nyomanka ki merangka ker kwama.
\v 13 Bulus kange farce cin tok kangi cin yabken bafuca yaken firjiya kange Bamfiliya mor nabire mwenge.
\v 14 Bulus kange farubcebo cin chu Firjiya kange Antakiya biten Bidiya fou ci do bikur wabe diye Asabaici cin yiken.
\v 15 Bwiko kiyeranka werfunero kange nob nuwa ka dukume, nobo du bi kur wabero tun tomange, ki kebyebo na kon wiki tomange na neka bikwan ce di kom toki.
\v 16 Bulus la kweni nunge ki kang, nobo Israila kange kom ki ne kwama durtiye kom nuwa.
\v 17 Kwama Israila, chok tenkwanub bebbo, la cin bwi firen Masar, la ki bi kwancer na duktankako ce, ci cokuciye.
\v 18 Bii ner kange ci kutantum curem kwini naar,
\v 19 Kambo cho twallum bitine niber wi biten Kan ana. ni tenkwanub bebo kwali.
\v 20 Dike wo gwam bwi curo kwini kwob na'ar tuddo kwini nung wo cume, kambo wuro kwama neci nob bolangeb, nimde nii dukume Samaila bou.
\v 21 Nobo keni a ne ci liya, kwama ne ci Shawulu bibwe Kish, ni naniyak Benjamin yilam liya curo kwini na'ar.
\v 22 Kwma kwmco dor kutile liyare nen, kum dauda yilam liya ciye. Dor Dauda kwama yiki man fiya Dauda bibwe Yesu niwo ner miro cwitiye an ma dike ma cwitiye gwam.
\v 23 Fou mor naniya ni wo kwama ceru ki nii fuloka Yesu, na wo co ma noro can mane.
\v 24 Wuro bwi nimde Yesu bou yahaya tok ker Yukwamwem kwamambo na yilokako ce wo nobo Israila.
\v 25 WoroYahaya dim nagen cerori co tok ki we kom kwatiye? make bo cho.
\v 26 Kebmibo bibei mor naniya Ibrahim, kange wo wab kwama ti more kume, ki bo ci tungu fulen folokako.
\v 27 Ki ker nobo yirangum Ursalima kange nobo tanki ciye, ci nyom cho bou cin dim tok ka nob to dukumtiye wo ci kiyeranti kakuk Asabaici fiye twalka ceko.
\v 28 bwen no dwalleu ci fiya dike bwi wo lam na bware ce dor cer cinken Bilatus a twallum cho.
\v 29 Kambo ci dim kwarub dike ci mulange dor cere, la cin cukum cho dor bwatiye ci yoken cho mor tuwe.
\v 30 Di kwama kum co mor bwiyare.
\v 31 Nobo bou wari kange ce feren galili kange Ursalima la cin ta to co ti kume kila. Nobo wuro ci warke ce nobonin nawo.
\v 32 Nyon bou kumen ki fulen wo lamlome, ker norowo ci ma tenkwanubebo neneu.
\v 33 Teluwe dobbinen noro. Nyo chon kum Yesu mor tuwe, nawo mor bifumereu Zabura na yobe cemo bi bwemi dwen ma yilam Tee mwe.
\v 34 Tak dike bwici kun cho tuwe co wo kari, bwi ceu fuyem tok ker nyo, man ne kom bibwiyer dauda wo wucaake bichom.
\v 35 Wo cho dike bwi co tok ker mor kange Zabura mani mwa dob nii wucakke mweti fuyem.
\v 36 kambo Dauda ma kwama ni wabe mor nire ce dike kwama cwitikye, ca bwiyam, cin furumco wari kange tenkwanubcebo, con fuyem.
\v 37 Di la nii wo kwama kunge to bo fuyeka.
\v 38 Kebmebo kom yomom fiye niwo wiyeu ci makumen fulen kere cutangka bwirang ke.
\v 39 Fiye co wiye gwam nii neken bilenke an fulom mor dike werfener Musa ko mani cokkom ti dor cereu.
\v 40 Na wo nyori kom yila ki cini kange dike nob nuwaka dukumeko toke kari bwi dor kumer.
\v 41 Kom nob cwikanka, kan lentanginker nyomankar take kan dim. wori mama nagen ti morkumeni kume, nangen do maka ciyati bwen ci yi komdi.
\v 42 Bulus kange Barnabas certiri nobo kenci ciya tok ten kerowo bidiye Asabaici wo botiye.
\v 43 Kambo wabe dime, Yahudawa kila kange wuro do bwanka Yahudawa co ci ne danne, ciya ma nangen luma kwama.
\v 44 Asabaici yilakangu cunnukuru bwirum na ci nuwa ker kwamaro.
\v 45 Di la yahudawa to mwer ka nobe ko, la cin dinki kor ci wengngum dike Bulus toke take cin ko.
\v 46 Dila Bulus kange Barnabas cin tok ker ki bi kwan manki gtai, ciki tamyo a ter yika kume ko ker kwamaro, Dauda kom tungume, kom nungi kom datenbo dume wo diriye na wo Nyori, nyan yilaken nobo kunmtacele nen.
\v 47 Nyo Teluwe dok nyo ki, man yo kom filang wiye nobo kuntacele wiye, na kom boki fulonka cwika dorbitinero nen.
\v 48 Nobo kumtacele nuwa nyori la cin ma bilantum, cin wab ker kwamaro gwam wuro ci ne fiyaka dume diri yiloten.
\v 49 Ker Teluwe wabi wi yare tinin bo cuwo.
\v 50 Dila Yahudawa cuk natubo kange ma wabe, nobo ken, kange nobo durtinim nabarubb wi cinanlore.
\v 51 Dila Bulus kange Barnabas fercinen ti kwero naci ke wi. cin cu cinanlor koniya.
\v 52 Nob bwankabo cin dim ki fuwor neret kange yuwa tangbe.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Ki kwama wo Bulus kange Barnabas doken bikur wabe yahudawa ri cin tok kero kambo numbo duce wo yahudawa kange Helinawa ne bilenke.
\v 2 La yahudawa buro nebo dureu cuuk nubo wo kumceleu ri dukci cin man funer kange keb cebo.
\v 3 La cin yi wi kumeni kila, ci tok ker cero ti kibi kwan neret wori bikwan kwamaro wi kange la cin ne yirome dor luma cero. Cin ma wuro ki yirome diker nyimang katini wo a mati kang Bulus kange Barnabas.
\v 4 Di la nubo cinan loreu kitangum kangen bo bwangten yahudawa kangumbo bwnagten nob tomangebo.
\v 5 Kambo nubo kunta cileu kange Yahudawa (wari kange dubo durtiniceu) cuwa naci neci dotange la naci mubang ci ki ter.
\v 6 Dila kambo ci nyumom nyeri, ciin cuwa cin cu cinanlor Likoniya, Listira kange Derbe, kange biten tini kentangum ciyeu.
\v 7 Fiye cii yoti kang tok ker kwamako nine.
\v 8 wi Listira, nii kange yim, manki bi kwan nace ko nin wori cin kilen cikko nee ce bou ceu ci yabo yam wi.
\v 9 Nii wo nuwam Bulus tok ker ti, Bbulus dok ti nuwece wi morece. Bulus fwel cenen ten nu la ci tori ciin bilenke naci fiya luma.
\v 10 La cin yi cho ki diro dur, kwenti dor na mwek.” La cho mwabiri ter yambo
\v 11 Kambo nubo mwerum duceuto dikero Bulus maneri, cin kung diro kiny Likoniya ciki, “Bweltimbo bou na noob lacin bow binen”.
\v 12 Ci cuo Barnabas ki “Zafsa” la bulus Hamisa wori co nii ci tok ker tii duceu.
\v 13 Liya wabe Zafsa wo bikur wabeer cero kino bwinko cinan loreu bou ti nenne kange funtini cibwati na latereu nyilo, co, kange nubo mwenim neu cui naci twi ciilen dikero ficange.
\v 14 Di la kambo nob tomangebo nuwa nyeri, ciinm worum kwilen cero, ri cin cerum mor mwerkanga nube ko nen wulom, ci kwa diroti.
\v 15 Ki “nubo ye bwi kom ma dikeroburo tiye? nyin nob ken, ki bwiyo dong-dong kange kumeu. Nyiki yi kom kero ken ri nako yilau bwanka dikeertinimbo bwirko buro ri nakom bwang ten kwama wo ki dumeu.
\v 16 Wo ywel dii kwama, dor bitiner wima kange dikero more ce gwam.
\v 17 Gwam kange wuro ci dob bo dor cero warka mani, ki co min mani yora ki mwem bo cine kom dii kwamau kange melako ki bi bwereu cin dim neer kumero ki cari kange bilangtum.
\v 18 La ki kero wo duwal Bulus kange Barnabas fiye bwei nyimde ci tim ki ci twika cinenek nuwanko ficange.
\v 19 Di la Yahudawa kangembo Antakiya kange Ikoniya bou la cin kwom neer nubero. ciin nubang Bulus ki ter ri la ciin kwob co ciin yaken kicho bwiko cinarlor, cii kwatiri cin bwiyam.
\v 20 Duwal kambo nob bwangka ko tirangum cunga ceke ri cin kwanum la cin doken cinan lor cel finiri cin chu darba kange Barnabas.
\v 21 Kambo tokka fullen kerero cinan loro curo kange fiya ka nob bwangka ceko ducceri, cin yilaken Listira, kange Ikoniya kange Antakiya.
\v 22 Ciin ti neka neer nob bwangkako bikwan ti naci ya yam mor bilenke, ki “Tam ban doken mor liyar kwama ki dotange duce.
\v 23 Kambo ci cikang nubo a bwangtenti kici mor ku wabe gwammeri, la cin kwobcinen dilo ki ngak-ngak ciin neken cii kang kwama, wo cii ne bilelnke cineneu.
\v 24 La cin cuken mor Bicidiya ci lam Bamfiliya.
\v 25 Kambo ci tokker cero Biriya, cin yira ken Italiya.
\v 26 Ci dob fiye co tiri, ciin yabken Antakiya mor mwege, fiye wo cii duk cii kang luma kwamak ki nangen do wo cii dim naweu.
\v 27 Ki kwamawo ci lam Antakiya ri cin mweer nubo ku wabe wariyeu, ciin yici dikero gwam wo kwama mani ki ciyeu, kange kambo ci wumom nure bilenke nubo kumtacileu ni neu.
\v 28 Cin yi wi kwitange kange nob bwangkabo.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 nubo kangembo yirau yahudiya cin bou Antakiya ri, ciin merang kebcebo nen, ki “Tano kom biye bo laro nawo werfun Musa ro tokkeri, mani ko fiya cerkati.”
\v 2 Wo dok Bulus kange Barnabas mor kobkangka kane ci. la cin cok Bulus kange Barnabas kange kangembo mre ce na cin ya Ursalima, cin wabkangi kange nobtomange bo, kange nubo durtinimbo dor meke wo.
\v 3 La nubo ku wabeu tom ci, cin cu mor finikiya kange Samariya la ciin yi cii yioka nubeko kumtacileu. ciin bou ki fuwor nerero dur fiye kebcebo wiye.
\v 4 Ki kwama wo ci bou mor Ursalima, nubo bi kurwabereu yoci kange nob tomangeebo, kange nubo durtinimbo, la cin yici dikero gwam wo kwama mani ki ci yeu.
\v 5 Di la nubo kangembo wone bilenke, wo ki more nob ding lingebeu, kweni tiri ciki, “Tamnyo a biye cinan lor, rina neci nyal ri naci bwangten werfuner Musa ro”.
\v 6 La nob bwangkabo kange nubo durko mweri wari naci to dike wor.
\v 7 Bwiko kwob kanka ko duce ri, Bitrus kweni tii ri, la yi ciki “Kem bibo, kom nyimom ki kwama duce cumeu, kwama ck ni more kume, la nyimi nubo kumtacileu a nuwa fulen kerer certiye, naci ne bilenke.
\v 8 kwama wo nyimom mor nereu, la yici ki yuwa tangbe co wucakke ci nee cii na wo ci ne beu.
\v 9 Ci tu bobo ki dimen kange ci la cin nirom ner cero ki belinke.
\v 10 La nyori, ye bwi ko cuwa kwama, la kom yo nob bwanka bonen ten tu tum ti, wo tebbeb kaka'a bo dolbo tu kake?
\v 11 Dila bin ne bilenke ban fiya fuloka ki luma nere kwama na ci ken.
\v 12 Nubo gwam tam cinge kambo ci nuwa Barnabas ti kange Bulus yici yirom boti kange diker nyimankako wo kwama mani tiber nubo kumtancileu kange ceke.
\v 13 kambo diim tokka kere kori, Yakubu ciya ki “Kebmibo, ko nuwa ye.
\v 14 Simon tok kambo kwama ki kaba ki lumanek tiikam nubo wo yim kumtacileu ri naci to dorcero nin nob more ce.
\v 15 Ke tinim nob tomangeb dukumero ciya kange wo, nawo mulangum meu.
\v 16 Bwiko dikero wo man yilau, ri man mutilo Dauda wi tak, wo yuram bitineu, man yila muti tiyak cekowi, nabi tiken ki cho.
\v 17 La nubo kumeu atin do kwama kange nubo kumta cileu gwam wo cico tiki dem mire.
\v 18 wo cho dike kwama tokkeu, wo ma dikero buro nyumom nanduweu.
\v 19 Nyori, mi tori bi nere nubo kumta cileu wo yilam kwama nineu dotange.
\v 20 Dila kange cinen tam nyo ciya dubom fulendo kange buro tumbo, kange wo ka biciro bwiyam bwiya.
\v 21 Wori ci tok ker ti mor werfun Musa mor cinan lor gwam ki kaltiro nanduweu la ciki kiyei mor bikur waber diye fobka gwam.
\v 22 La yor nob tomnagebonen kange nubo durko kange nubo bikur wabe ro nen gwammeu na ci chok Yahuza cwoti ki Barsabbas kange cila buro no nubo dor kebcebeu. la cin tom Antakiya kange Bulus Barnabas.
\v 23 cin mulangi ki kangcek fiye nob tomangebo, kange nubo durko, keb kumebo, ki kebnyebo wo no kumtacileu mor Antakiya, Siriya, Ciliciya, Yarume.
\v 24 wori nyim nuwa kangem nubo ceri fou nyinen, kebo ki yomka nyek, la cin kwomcang kom ki keti ro kange kumen nereu.
\v 25 Nyitori yori kabo nyo wo nyane dume ne wine nanyi cok nubo kangem ri nanyi tomci kumen kange nubo nyi cui cuiyeu Barnabas kange Bulus.
\v 26 Nubo wo neken dume ceu ki Teluwer bek Yesu Kiriti.
\v 27 La nyin tom yakubu kange Silas wo, ayikom dike coti win ken ki mor kere ce.
\v 28 Wori yori kabo yuwa tangbe kwamakonen kang nyo ri, nyi yo kumen deben do dur wo la dikero wo tam a bwang tenneu.
\v 29 Di kom dubom dike cii neken bibwiteu, noka bwiyale, woka biciro bwiyam bwiyau, kange buroka. No kom dubom dikero buro ri, kan yi kwamer.
\v 30 La ciin kambo ci yalammeri, yirau antakiya, kambo ci mweru nubo duce wariyeri, ciin neken cii mulangkako.
\v 31 Ki bwikob kiyekako ri, ciin bilangi ki bikwan nere ro.
\v 32 yahuza kange wo nob tomangeb dukumek takeu ne nubo bi kwan neret ki keti duce, ri la cin fiya bi kwan.
\v 33 kambo ci darang kume tini wiyeri, ciin yoken cii ki fuwor neret nubo co nen, na ci yilaken nubo tomou ciye nen.
\v 34 Dila cila tori yori kabo ci tim wi.
\v 35 Dila Bulus kange Barnabas tim Antakiya (kang tangum kebcebo duce) ci ki merang cinen ti ri, ci tok ker kwamaro ti.
\v 36 Kambo kume tini ri Bulus yi Barnabas ki' na weu “bi yila nabi yarum kebbebo mor Cinanloro gwam wo ni tok ker kwamareu, nabi to keno ci mati nyi ri”.
\v 37 Barnabas cui naci tu Yahaya cii cuo ti ki Markus ce kange ci.
\v 38 Dila Bulus kwabi ri, ki yorbo cia tu Markus, wo dubom cii mor Bamfiliya ri yabo kab tak kange ci nagen do nineu.
\v 39 La kwob kangkako dou tiber cer, la bou ki yal kanka bwitici, Barnabas tu Markus kane co la yab mwmbo ciin yaken kuburus.
\v 40 Dila Bulus cok cica can ciin cu, bwiko dulo ko kebcebo kwocinen, neken cii kang luma kwama.
\v 41 La cin yaken mor Syria kange Cilicia, ci nee nubo bikur wabere bikwan neret ti.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 Bulus tak bou Darbe kange listira, la nii bwankako kange co ti ki Timoti wiwi, bibwe nawiye Yahuda wo nii bilenke, dila Tee ce Baheline.
\v 2 Cii tok dikero kenti dorcer nyi nubo wo Listira kange Ikoniya.
\v 3 Bulus cui naci ya yam kange co, la cin to cho, cin biye cinen laro ker yahudawa wo fiye tini curo nineu. wori gwamce nyimom ki tece nii heline.
\v 4 Kambo ci cukenti mor cinanlore, ciin nerang nyal tinimbo nob tomangebo wo kange. nubo dur tinimbo wo mor Ursalima ciya cike ri, naci bwangten.
\v 5 La nubo bikur wabereu fiya bikwan neret mor bilenke la ciin kila cii cobten ti diye ki diye.
\v 6 Bulus kange nubo tikan co tiyeu ya mor cungko Phrygia kange Galatiaya, wori yuwa tangbe kwamako ywanmci tokka ker cero cunga ko Asia.
\v 7 Ki kwama wo cii bow bidom kange Misiyari, cii cuwa na ci do mor Bitiniya, dila yuwa tangbe Yesu ywamci.
\v 8 Kambo ci dou Mysia ri, ciin yirau mor cinanlor Troas.
\v 9 Bulus ma dukumbo ki kume; nii Makidoniya tiim wi, kinong coti ki, “Bou fou Makidoniya na mwi tikang nyo”.
\v 10 Kambo Bulus to dumeri, dangjang do naci yaken Makidoniya, cin kwabi nercer ki kwama cuo nyo nyi tok ker cero Makidoniya.
\v 11 Kambo ci dob mor Troas ri, nyin yaken ciyer nyin yaken Samothrace, la cel fini ceri nyin bow Neapolis.
\v 12 La nyi kwen wiri nyin cuo Philippi, wo co cinan lor Makidoniya, cinan lor la tangnumbo mor biten Roma; La nyin cerum wi cinan lor nen kume ni kila.
\v 13 Ki diye fobka Yahudawa ri nyin cer ken nyilo cinan lor kong chaci ki kwa nere ki nysn fiya fiye kwobka dilo wi. La nyin yiken ri, nyon tok ker. kange natubo wo mwerum wiyeu.
\v 14 Nawiye kange dendo ki Lidiya, wo wiye kwilen tiyeu, ci ceru cinan lor Tiyatira, wo wab kwamatiyeu, cuwa tu nuwa nyo. La Teluwe wumom neer cero cin cuwa tu ki dike Bulus tok tiyeu nen.
\v 15 Kambo co kange nubo loceri, cin kenyo ciki, no kom ciya komki min yilam ki bilenke kwama nin di kom bou ko cerum lomi. “La cin dok nyo nyin ciya.
\v 16 Nyori, ki kwamawo nyin yaken ti fiye kwob ka diloke, bibuya canga kange woki ninga tokake wab kang nyo. Ci bou teluwe ce nen ti ki kyemer ducce ki to kako ci totiyeu.
\v 17 La bubiya wo bwnag ten Bulus ti kange nyo la ci kwabang dir, ti ki “Nubo buro cangab kwama dureb. ciki yi kom nure fuloka”.
\v 18 Ciki mai nyo ki kume tini kila. Dila kambo Bulus kangum neer cero kayam meri, yi kangi la yico “mi nyal nenti ki den Yesu Kiristi, ceru cinen”. La ciin cerum ki kwama co.
\v 19 Kambo teb teluweb cebo tori yoka neerek fiya ka mweb kemerceu cuwe ri, ciin tam Bulus kange cila kwob kanci yaken ki cii fiye tubo miyem diker tiye kabum nob bolangeb.
\v 20 kambo ci bou ki ci ka bum nob bolangebri, cii ki “Nubo buro kum cnag cinan lor beroti. ciin yahudawa.
\v 21 Cii merang nure ti wo kebo dong-dong kange dike nubo Roma ciye ciya cuko naci bwang tenneu.
\v 22 La mwerkan nubo ko gwam kwinang Bulus ce kange Silas, nob bolangebo wob rangum kwilen cero cii nen ri ne nyallo naci makanci ki Belyange kwamangi nyeu.
\v 23 Kambo malli ciyeri? Ciin dokken cii mor Furcina, ri ciin yi nii to furcina tiyeu na kii ca kum cii yorak.
\v 24 kambo ci yo nyallo weri, nii to ka Furcinako dokken cii kuwe more ri cin kum na tini ceko.
\v 25 Kina ciinkume Bulus kange Silas, kwob dilo rila cii ka nuwe wabka kwama tii la tangnum nubo furcinau cuwa tuu nuwa ciiti.
\v 26 Dang jangri ka mikanka dor bitiner wo dok kwar kur furcinau mikangume la danjang nyilok tininmbo gwam womangum kang nubo bwambwabeu kwiya.
\v 27 Nii to furcinatiyeu yuram dumbo ri, cin to nyiloko wumom, la cin co ku kulen cero ri, cin cui naci twallum dor cero, wori cin kwabi ki nubo furcinau cirangum.
\v 28 La Bulus kwa cinen dir kibi kwan ki, “Nuware dor mwe ro nen twirak, wori nyin wi fou gwam nye.
\v 29 Nii to furcina tiyeu me naci bo cinen ki kirak, la cin doken mor wulom mor taiye, ciin cungi kabum Bulus kange Silas.
\v 30 La ciin coku ci kaleri, ciki “Nubo dur miik nye ma mati nami fiya fuloka?
\v 31 Ciin yico ki “Neken bilenke teluwe Yesu nen, namwi fiya fuloka mo kang nubo lomeu gwam.
\v 32 Ciin yico ker Teluwero, kange nubo loceu gwam.
\v 33 La nii yo furcina tiyeu tu ci ki kume cuo, la cin nirom dercero, ri co loce gwam cin yum mwem kwamam bo dang jang.
\v 34 la kambo ci bou ti Bulus kange Silas loco ri, ci tik cinen carito kaciye, cin bilangi ducce kange nubo mor luwe ceu, wori cin ne bilenke kwama nen.
\v 35 La kambo fini celumeri, nob bolangebo tom nobo to cinanlor tiye nen ker, ciki “Dob nubo co a yaken ti”.
\v 36 nii to furcinan tiyeu yi Bulus kero couki “Nob bolangebo tunguo tomange minen na dob kom ko yakenti. na weu dila kom ceru ri nako yakenti ki luma.
\v 37 Dila Bulus kane silas ciya cinen ki “Cii malli nyo nyanglang bolang mani, ri nyi nubo Roma keneu- la ciin mer ken nyo mor furcina. La ciki cui wona weu naci yoken ki yurangka ka? mani nyo! Ciya bou ki bwici naci cok nyo kale”.
\v 38 La nii to kakkawo ya yi nob bolangebo kereburo. Kambo ci nuwa ki Bulus kange Silas nubo Roam ri cin cuwam tai.
\v 39 Nob bolangebo bou la ciin ken ci rila cii cokangum kale, la cin yici ki ciya cerum mor cinan loro nen.
\v 40 La Bulus kange Silas cerangum furcina ri cin bou to Lidiya. Kambo Bulus kange Silas to nuberi, ciin neci bikwan neret, cin dubom cinan loro.
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 Kambo cin cum biten Amfibolis kange Aboloniya, cin lam biten Tasaloniya ka, fiye lo kwama yahudawa wiyeu.
\v 2 Bulus, kambo cilerumeu yakenti cinen tokanti kange ci kume nukune kiriti taar, mor bifumer tinim.
\v 3 Bulus wumom bifumero yici ki, “Atam nyo Kiristi anuwa dotange, an kunum mor tuwe yici ki “inco Yesu miyikom ti inco kiristi.
\v 4 Kangum Yahudawa ciya cin bwangten Bulus kange Silas, kange Helinawa, Kange nubo kumtacile neken dor cereu duce kange natubo dur tinim kebo bi duwar.
\v 5 yahudawa biro nebo bilenke cin dim ki kurom, cin tokangum nob kutumebo fiye mi yeka kange tenka, cin kum kutumeu mor cinan lor, nubo ducce bwang ten citi. yacin ter kiyando lo Yesu nen, cin cokum Bulus kange Silas kabum nubem.
\v 6 Dila citobo Bulus kange Silas cin kwob kangum Yason kange nob bwanka kwamam ko kange yaken kici kabum nob bolonageb mor bitinenceu, ciyiti ki, Birombo nubo kunene nubertiye, wo cin bou binen.
\v 7 Nubo wuro Yason yociyeu cin fuwam werfun Kaisar, ciyiti liyakange wi dendo Yesu.
\v 8 Kambo nubo kange nob bolnagebo nuwa nyeri, lan kwomci.
\v 9 kambo ciyo kenero Yason nir kange tangne nubori, lacin nyamkan cinen.
\v 10 Mor kumewo nob kwamabo cokum Bulus kang. Silas, cin twomci biten Biriya. kambo ci lameri, cin doken mor lo kwama yahuda.
\v 11 Nubo Biriya kidimen kange nubo Tasuliska, cin ciya kange ker Bulus cero kinero win. Cifuwa bifumer kwamaro ti kumeni kumeni, wori na cin yimon ker Bulus. Yora. keno bilenkeri.
\v 12 Naweu la nubo ducce morece cin ne bilenke wari, kange natub helinawa wo, cin yimom kange nabarubo ducce.
\v 13 kambo yahudawa wo tasaloniyawa cinuwa ki Bulus tok ker kwamaroti Biriya cin yaken wi firen, cin kun ner nubero.
\v 14 Dang jang nob kwamabo Biriya to Bulus twam ken caji cin dubo silas kange Timoti bwiri.
\v 15 Birombo wo yati ki Bulus tuu co kutan biten Antina. kambo ci dob Bulus wiyeri, cin yo tomange, cinen wo Silas ce kange Timoti na cin bou cinen wolum no nure wiri.
\v 16 kambo Bulus ningtan boka Silas koti kange Timoti Atina kangum ner mor nerece, kambo cito bitineco dimki bibwiti tinim.
\v 17 Cin fuwanangi kange yahudawa lo kwama kange nubo wab kwamamtiyeu, kange birombo citiye kirkireu, fiye miyake kange tenka.
\v 18 Dila kange Abikuriyawam nob nyomkab wabkang kange co. Kangumbo yiki “Nyewo niwo tokker nyeu ki tok kiye?” kangembo yiki “Cin cerkan ni kange wo co nubo ti na bwang ten fulendo fwereu,” Wori ci tok ker Yeesu roti kange kwenka ceko tuweu.
\v 19 Cin Bulus cin yaken ciko diko Arassa, ciyitiki, mwo nyin yo merangka ko wo mwe fwerko woka?
\v 20 Kertinimbo mutikan tiyeu, fiye nyinen. Nyi cwiti na nyimom dike kerowo dan tiyeu”.
\v 21 (Antimiyawa) kange fabubo more ceu, cine dor ciro kang tikangka dikero fwirtinim kange tangnim cem.
\v 22 Bulus tiken tiber dii Arasa yiki, “Kom nubo Aniniyawa min nyimom kom nob bikwaneb fuleneb.
\v 23 Min ynimom kambo kom ki wabre kwama kimeu min bwelangtiyeu, dila minto tang lando kange dikero mulangum wi dorce tokktiki, “Kwama wo wuro cin nyombeu.” Miki tok dike kom wabti mor bwininyomkau.
\v 24 kwama ywel dor bitinero kange dike moreceu, kambi cin co kwamam diyeu kange bitineu, mani yi lo kwama wuro nubo mu ki kang cikeu.
\v 25 Mani do tikaliti kange wo labou a neco tiyeu, kange fubom kange dikero wuyak.
\v 26 Nii win nin ci fwel nubo dor bitinere gwam, naci yi dor bitiner, co ci nung kume ciya mati dor bitinere kange yika tini fiye ciya yim tiye.
\v 27 Naci do kwama, tano ciya do cori, naci fiya co. Bwenno ci kutangbo beneneu.
\v 28 Biyim morece binuwa luma bekti, kambo kange mi nyomka more kume toke. “Bo bibyo loce.
\v 29 Nno bi bei kwama ri, datenbo bi mwer kang kwama kange mwin kaka no kokaa banatini, kange tini wo ci ywirangeu.
\v 30 Dila nyori, kwama turingum kumeni bwini nyom ka, dila cin tokker nubokwarub adubom bwinraka kereko.
\v 31 Kuniwi wo ciyo ca ma dorbitinenereu win bolang tiyeu mor bilenke, ki niiwo ci cokeu. Kwama dang nii co ki kunka ceko tuwe.
\v 32 kambo nubo Atina nuwa ker kwenka tuweri, kangem bo buo Bulus kangem bo ki. “Nyan nuwa tenen tak, dor kerero wonen.
\v 33 Lanyori Bulus dubomci.
\v 34 Dila nabarubo kangum bo morece ciya ki ker kwamaro, cin ne bilenke, mworum kange diyoni Siyus in ni durlor. Dii Arasa kange nawiye kange deudo damaris kangum bo wari, kange ci.
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 Bwiko dike buro ko gwam di Bulus dubom Antakiya yaken Koranti.
\v 2 La wi ca wab kan kange bayafude kange dendo Akila, bwe bitine Buntus bou ti bowe Italiya kange wice Balkisu. wori kalaudiya tok kero ki nyial Yafudawa a dubom Romawu. Bulus ya cinen.
\v 3 la wori nangen ciro win con yi kange ci co managen. wori cin nob yuwel ka teneb.
\v 4 La nyo Bulus ti yai ku wabe kakuk fobka co cuiti na co fiya ciya Yahudawa kange Elenawa.
\v 5 kambo Silas kang Timoti lam Makidoniya ri, Bulus neken dorcero kero min, warker Yafudawa nen Yesu co Kristi.
\v 6 La kambo Yafudawa kunang cinenten, ci to coti Bulus chokum belle ceu kaci la yii cia bwiyale kumeu a yila dor kumer. Man cerum nawo kange kab maki yan nob kumta cilenen.
\v 7 La chon dobum ci con cu lo Titus, Justus nii wo wab kwamam tiye. Loceu bidom kange ku wabeu.
\v 8 Ki pu nii dur wuu wabero ne bilenker Teluwe nen, kange nubo loceu, la korangtiyawa dorcereu ne bilenker la cin yuu cinen mwem kwamambo.
\v 9 Kwma yii Bulus ki kume mor dukume cuwa re tai, tokkero kendo.
\v 10 La min wi kange mo, kange nii mani a nuwa mwen twirak tiye wori min wi ki nob ducce fou mor cinan loro wo.
\v 11 Bulus da wi na coro win kange cuiyakko nukkun, merang ker kwamamroti more ciye.
\v 12 kambo Galiyo yilam nii tamki Akaya, Yafudawa kwenang Bulus nin ten wo llam ci yaken ki co kabum bolangeu.
\v 13 Niwo bolum nubo ti na wab kwama, kidimen kange werfun do.
\v 14 La kambo Bulus ki naco tok keredi, Galiyo toki, yi Yafudawa kom “Yafudawa na ki kero bwirko ca maneu na dur di mitin warkero.
\v 15 la buro kan me ke dor kered kange denti kange wer fun kumer, ko tokkan wo bwitikom. Ma cuibo yila nii bolange dor ketitowo.
\v 16 Galiyo dok ci a kwenum fiye boulange nen.
\v 17 la nyeu ci ta sactanicu inya bi kur wabero ci buk co kabum kutile buolange. La galiyo karbo diker ci maneu.
\v 18 Bulus kambo yiwi kumeni kila nyeu lan dubom kebcebo yaken Suriya. Mor nabire mwenge kange Balkisu kange Akila la na co dob fiye nabire mwenge tum nob ti cankuriyari, con cerum yiri doreceu. wori con tuu nor Banazare.
\v 19 Kambo ci bou Aficari, Bulus dubom Balkisu kange Akila wi, la ceu bwicui con yaken mor bi kur waber Yafudawar con fuwakangi wari.
\v 20 La cin me Bulus na yim kange ci kumtinidi, la ciyabo.
\v 21 Ta nure ce dob ci lam yi ci man yila ten kumen na kwama ciyari. La con doken nabire mwenge wi Afisa.
\v 22 Kambo Bulus Yiram kai cariyari, la con kwi con yarum ku wabeu wursalima la con yira ken Antakiya.
\v 23 Bwiko co yim wi kumeni kilamri, Bulus taa nure ce yaken cinan loro Galatiyawa kange Firjiya la ne bi bei tomangeu bikwan nerer.
\v 24 La wi kange bayafude dendo Afolos wo ci bou ce Iskandariya bou Afica, chon nii nyomka ker kwamar.
\v 25 Afolos Cin ne merangka wo teluwe ceu. Nii bikwan yuwa tangbek. coki tok dong dong dikero dor Yesu reu. la chon nyomom ka yuu ka mwenge yuwanak.
\v 26 Afolos ter tok ka kere ki kibi kwan mor bikur waber. La kambo Balkisu, kange Akila nuwa ceri, cin cou cho chunga la cin fwetang cinen nure kwama kambo ken.
\v 27 La kambo cho cwui na cho cuken Akaya la kebcebo ne bo bi kwan neerer, la ci mu lang bibei tomange wo Akaya na ci yoco, kambo ca yiram meri, con Tikan nubo buro ne bilenker ki luma ducce.
\v 28 Afolos Yafudawa diker nyumanka kange bikwan do cho cikeu nungi kero nin la Yesu co Kristi
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Afolos firen koranti, Bulus kentangum bitine diyele con bo cinanr lor Afisa. fou tak co fiya kangem nob bwanka.
\v 2 Bulus yici kom yo yuwa tangbe ka fiya kom ni bilenke cin ciya, o-ong nyo nuwambo fulen yuwa tangbeko wucakke wi.
\v 3 Bulus la ki yuka mwenge ko wini kom mane, ciki yuka mwenge Yahaya.
\v 4 Bulus ciya ki yahaya ma nubo nen yuka mwenge yiloka, yiki kom ne bilenke wo a boti bwiti bwiko cek, Yesu.
\v 5 Nubo nuwa nyori, co ci yu cinen mwembo ki den teluwe Yesu.
\v 6 Di la Bulus yoti kanko dor cer dila yuwa tangbeko wucakke, yirau dor cer, cin tok ker kange nyitin kange to ka dukume.
\v 7 Cin dim bi kate kwob shilombo yob.
\v 8 Bulus doken kor bi waber co merangti ki bi kwan bwiyer na cuka taar ce. bwantenti ci mor fowaka keret, co fwetang nubonenti ciya ne bilenke, dor dike tabi na liyar kwamaro ce.
\v 9 Dila kangem yahudawa bongum, cin ko bwankako, di cin yoten kanka nure Almasiya kabum mwerka nobek. Nyori Bulus kwab cinen wari kange nubo ne bilenke, yoten merangkako mor merangka Tyrannus.
\v 10 Nyo co matiye dim curo yob, yaken biten Asia nuwan ker kwamaro, yahudawa kange Helinawa.
\v 11 Kwama ma nangen do dur kan Bulus.
\v 12 Wo nubo nuwa bo luma fiya luma twirak ciyeko dim. yowako bwiko ciru nubo nen, ninga, kange kelkelito, yuwako bwirko ci cerangum bwi nobe. La cin yo lalang kwabka bwi Bulus ce.
\v 13 Yahudawa kangem nub bowab wi cin dob fiye co neneu, cin tu dor cero nin na cin ma nange ki den Yesu, ciki nyo dokkom mor den Yesu wo Bulus ma biwerer cerotiye, kom cerum”.
\v 14 Nubo ma dike wo ci bi neber, bibeyo lo nii wabe durko kange bweyude dendo Sceva wii kibi bei niber wo ma dikero wo tieyu.
\v 15 Yuwako bwirko kari ki ma nyomom Yesu, ma nyomom bulus la kumeu, bi we?
\v 16 La yuwako bwirko bwirko mor nii kwenancinenten lam ci cok, ci cer wi ku we cuwo kwancer ki deti.
\v 17 Wuro yilam dike nyomom nyome fiye nubo wiye gwam, Yahudawa kange Helenawa nubo yim Afisa. Cin nuwa tai kambo ken, den teluwwe Yesu fiya duktangka.
\v 18 Nob bwankabo dutce tak, ci bo ci kiye nangendo bwirko ci mane.
\v 19 Nob buwabo cin bo ki bifumer ciyero cin twirangum kabum nobem wo ci kiye dike a tatiye, Lam bikate kwini nung na mwindo ce.
\v 20 La ker kwamaro yalati kibi kwan nure dutce.
\v 21 Kambo Bulus dim nangen cero na bibweret kwamaroce Afisa, yuwa tanbgeko bwanten ki co nure Makidoniya kange Akiya dor nuret, cin yaken Ursalima, co ki, Bwiko ma ferenne, tamyo ya Roma.
\v 22 Bulus twom bibei tomange ce yob, Timoti, kange Erastus, firen Makidoniya, nobuwo tikan ceu.
\v 23 Di la co ki bwici con nintanci firen Asiya nyobi dob. Dila kobkankako dur kweni afisa ker dor nure do wo.
\v 24 Knage nii kwabi dendo Dimatrayus wuro Tuu fulen bwiner tiye wo Diyana ce, wo nangendo bo nob kwabi to nin ti fiya ka kambo ken.
\v 25 La cin mwer nub kwabiyo yici ki, kom nyomom ki kwabiyo wo bo fiya kiyemer doka ti dutce.
\v 26 Kom to, kom nuwa ki kebo ka afisa, dila gwam biten asiya Bulus wo bolom nubo dutce. Yiti ki “Fulen da kange mani ci yweltiki kange”.
\v 27 Kebo kwabi beto a fiyakomkati ki kwace, dila bikur fulen bero Diyana durku a yilam manki nangen. Nyon ca lem dur cero. Co kange biten Asiya gwam, Kange dorbitiner wabko tiye.
\v 28 Di cin nuwa nyori, ci mam funer kambo ken, cin co bi cor ki diro kwamer “Nii dur co Diyana wo Afisa”.
\v 29 Cinan loro gwam dim ka bwali, nubo tibranbo yaka fiye mwerka. Fiya cuwo cin tam far yame ce Bulus, Gayus, kange Aristarchus, borombo bou Makidoniya.
\v 30 Bulus mani naco do mor nobe, di nob bwanka cebo yuwanco.
\v 31 Nyo farub Bulus cebo kangembo wo nubo durtinim yare Asiya cin tom cinen ki kemi kwam kwame ca dore tare.
\v 32 Kange nob cuk kange dikerti, kangem ken cuk kange dikerti, wori nobe kweri nero kayam. Dutce more ce nyombo ye bwi ci mwere.
\v 33 Kangem mor nubo yi Iskandari wo Yahudawa cin tung ti kabbeu, dila Iskandari cerou kung kang ceko ki ciya kumom, cwiti na ci yi nubo mwerom meu ker.
\v 34 Di la kambo ci nyomom co Bayahude di gwam ciye cin kun kiyange na kang keneko yobece ci tok ti ki, “Dur ki no fiye Artimas wo Afisa.”
\v 35 Di nii mulankako cinanloro cwo nou dor nobere, la co ki, kom nubo Afisa, we nyombo ki Afisa tiberowo fulen (Allaliri) nii dur kange fulen do yaru firen dii kwama?
\v 36 Di la ci kanang bo dike weu, daten kom kumom, kom mare kange diker kutti kutti.
\v 37 Kom bo ki nubo wuro fou ku bolange, kebo dur cin nob kob, na mor bi kur wabe, kaka nob dilakab fiye kwama be wiye.
\v 38 Tano Damatriyas kange nob kwabito wari kange ciye nan wiki kange ker dor kange ku bolange wi wumom wume, nob bolange bo wiranagi, ci a ya ki kiyange bwitici.
\v 39 Tano kero kange wi na toka ko ceri an do tiber ciro fou mwerka beko, bo yiti dok-doke.
\v 40 Bilenke boki no mor bitore kange kwalkanke wo bwi duweneu. bo manki dike ba torti dor dike wo bwiye, co tok nyori co, ci yo nobe.
\v 41 Kambo ca nuwa nyori la con dob nubo yalkange.
\c 20
\p 
\v 1 kambo kwalkake dimeri Bulus twomi a cou bibei tomange, la con neci bikwan nerer. La con ne ci nacume can dubom ci coki, Makidoniya.
\v 2 kambo co ya bitene ceri, con yi nob bwanka bo ker bikwaner, La con biyeken biten Helenawa.
\v 3 kambo ca mam cuikko taar wiyeri, yafudawa ma cinen biciren kambo co dadom ca kwina bire mwenge tiye na co yaken Suriya. la con fulogum neer cero yila ken Makidoniya.
\v 4 Nubo yuo cho Asiau, mwerkange Sabatarus, bibwe Buru, Biriya gayus, bibwe Derbi, Timoti kange Antakus, kange Sakundu, gwam ciye nob bwankab Tasalonika, Kange Tikikus, kange Trophimus wo Asia.
\v 5 La nubo buro cuken ten nyinen la ci nintang nyo Taruwasa.
\v 6 kambo na do nabire mwenge Filippi bwiko kumerek carito man ki cam fuwam meu. La cin yii wi kume niber.
\v 7 Kume kaba kumeni kiyang cari teri, Bulus yi nob bwanka bo ker, co cuiti na kubo celfini, la con kwob kercero cuwemje lam cin kume.
\v 8 Kirako wi kila kuwe diyewo nyo mwerkangum wiyeu.
\v 9 La cerangeu bwe kange yimwi dendo Eutychus, wuro yarken dumbo tu'u cou, kambo Bulus tok keroti cuwemi bwe bwayile wo dam dumeu, yuram, bitine con bwiyam.
\v 10 La Bulus yirau ri toki ki, kange nii akwomde dor cer, dume wi bwiyabo.
\v 11 lacon kwiken luwediyeu tak, cinkabkanghum ci cam.'
\v 12 chin bou ki bweu ki dume lachin fiya birom nere kebo bi duwar.
\v 13 la nyo yakenten Bulus nin kina bire munghe nyon doken Assos, nyon cwi na nyo tum Bulus kina bire. wonco dike cocwi maka, con cwi naco yakina.
\v 14 kambo ci fiya nyo Assos ri nyon tumco mor nabire mwenghe nyin yaken metelina.
\v 15 Bwiko kwenka nyeko firen celfini ce nyo bou diyele kiyo celfini tak nyon bou cinanloro militu.
\v 16 La Bulus tuken cuu kako Afisa mor na bire mwenghe. kati yilo co tengum dorcer Asiya, wori co kayamti. na mam di bi dii kakuk fenticon na fiya co wursalima.
\v 17 Wi militu con tom nabarub ya afisa na cou cinen nubo durko ku wabe.
\v 18 Kambo ci bou cinenri, con yi ci ki “Kom ki bwikom kom nyumom, Tabti ki diye kaba ma dokum na'a Asiyau, kambo ma twal kumeti kange komeu.
\v 19 Min bwang teluwe ninenten ki lomjume nee kange mwem, mor boulange wo fiya yero ki biciren, Yafudawa bou.
\v 20 Kom nyumom ma nuwa bou tuu ka nan yikom dike a ma kumen tiye, min bwang kumenten luwe ma merang kumen dikero ti yanglang.
\v 21 Kom nyumom kambo ma werang Yafudawa ti kange Helenawa dor yiloka kwama, kange biten ker fiye teluwe Yesu.
\v 22 La na weu miki yang wursalima yuwa tangbe kwamako mung men ti nyang lang tam in ya, ma nyombo dike a fiyayeti fireneu.
\v 23 La Yuwa tangbeko nung menti cinan loro gwam bwanka kange dotange nintang ye ti.
\v 24 La ma tubo dumemi wiki kange nangen minen, nan dim cuak ko knage nangen do ma yo fiye teluwe Yesu, na tokka fulen ker luma.
\v 25 Na weu kom to, min nyumom kom gwam, bouro ma yiciker liyar kwamareu, mani ka toyeti tak.
\v 26 la min yimkom ki diye no, miman ki bwiyale ni dur mir.
\v 27 Wori ma nuwa tutum nan yikom kange dike kwama cuiti kumeneu.
\v 28 Na cori ko ta dor kumero kange nob bwangkabo wo yuwa tangbe kwama yokom nubo dur cereu. beko cobi, ko to kuu wabe kwamau, wo ca ten ki bwiyale ceu.
\v 29 man nyumom bwiko ma kubomtiyeu, Bifumeru me kangem an dou (Nob yulaneb) more kume mani cia dob kwama ten do ti.
\v 30 Man nyumom bwen no more kumeri kangum nob an kweri an toker kerti to bwirangi nyeu na kom bibei tomange bwiyocik.
\v 31 Na ceu ko yi yim cobkam, ko kwabi ki coro taar man dobbo yika kumek kererk. kange mwem kume kange kakuk.
\v 32 Na wonyeu ma dob komti kange kwama kange ker luma cero, wo bi kwan mu ka kumekeu, lana ne ten kom kwali wari kange nuboburo wi mor kwama cokum gwammeu.
\v 33 Ma dillanbo nuwe ki kanan mwin kange kulen.
\v 34 Mo ki bwimo mom nyumom kanko wo ki ma diker min cuiti mani kange nubo wo kange meu.
\v 35 Dikero gwam min yikom dikero ka ma tikaliti cikeu, kange dike ka mam nangen do ti cikeu, na kom kwa ki ner kerero wo Teluwe Yesu kibwki cho tokeu, wi ki fiyaka dutce.
\v 36 kambo ca dim tokakeri, chon chungi dor nurer chin kwob dilo ti.
\v 37 Nub ciwiye wi kila, cin ne Bulus kwendowe kange cwika cek.
\v 38 La cin kangum ner ki dikero wo cha tikeu, ki mani ciya tou choti tak. La chin yo cho mor na bire.
\c 21
\p 
\v 1 kambo nya yalkang kange ciyeri nyon doken mor nabire mwenge nyon ta nure cinanlor koceu. Celfini la nyon lam Rodusa, wi la nyon yaken cinan loro Batara.
\v 2 Kambo nyo fiya nabire mwenge yab ken ti Phoenicia, la nyon doken.
\v 3 Kambo nyon tou kibru tiyeu, nyon dubom kan ko mokenyeu, nyon mer dor Suriya, nyo yira cinan lorp Taya, wori nabire mwenge a cer kulen cero wi.
\v 4 Kambo nyo fiya bibei tomange, la nyo yiwi kume niber, la bibei tomange yii Bulus, ki yuwa tangbe yare wursalima.
\v 5 Bwiko kumetinen nyon yoten kang yam nyon bo min. gwam ciye kange natub ci bo kange bibeiyo lociyeu cin yo nyo bwim cinan lor. Co la nya cung cungi kong caji nyo kwob dilo.
\v 6 Nya ne kang na cungme kange ci. La nyon doken nabire mwenge, ci kange natub cibo cin yilaken lo.
\v 7 Kambo nyo dim yim nyembo taya di nyon lam talamaya. La wi, nyo yar kan kange kebnyebo nya da kume win kange ci.
\v 8 Celfini nyon kweni nyon cuu kaisariya. nyo donken lo Philip be nine fulen ker tiye, win mor nobe nibereu, nyon yii kange co.
\v 9 La nii wo wiki bibeyo na'ar, bibutob wo tok ker dukumer tiyeu.
\v 10 Kambo nyo yii wi kumeni biduwareri, kange nii dukume bou mor Yahudawa den cero Agabus.
\v 11 Bou nyi nen tuu dak Bulus ko, la bwam nace kange kange ceko, la co toki, yuwa tangbe kwamako toki, nyo Yahudawa a bwa nii dakkewo tiye, la ci an neken cho kang nob kumtacile.
\v 12 Kambo nya nuwa dikero buro di, nyo kange nubo yim wiyeu ken Bulus a yare wursalima.
\v 13 La Bulus yici, ye kom matiye, ko ci wuyeti kom kimen bikwan nertiye? La min ciya kebo ka bwaka, la nan bwiyam wursalima, ki den “Teluwe” Yesu.
\v 14 Kambo Bulus mani a ciyatiyeri, nyon dubom ci ka wiyeko, la nyon toki, dike Teluwe cuitiye a ma nyo.
\v 15 Kambo kumeni wo nyon tu cuayelyeu, nyon kwiker wursalima.
\v 16 Kangem bibei tomange kaisariya cin bou kange nii ci choti ki Mnason, nii kubru, ni yuloka kabo, wuri nya yiiti kange ceu.
\v 17 Kambo nya lam wursalima di, kebyebo nyo ki fuwor nerer.
\v 18 Celfini ceri, Bulus ya kange nyo fintano Bitrus wiyeu, nubo durco wi gwam.
\v 19 Kambo cha yarum ciyeri, la con yii ki winti dike kwama mani mor nubo yim kumtacileu, ki nangen cero.
\v 20 Kambo ci nuwa di cin duktang kwama la cin yii co mon to yii be mbo bikaten kilam wo ne bilenker kange Yesu mor Yafudawa, na cin bwangten werfunero.
\v 21 La cin yii dor mwer, mo merang yahudaa yim tiber nob kumtacileu ci cutang ker Musa ro wi, la mun yi ci abiyetende lar bibeyero, ci a bwangten de dambo carko.
\v 22 Ye bama tiye? bicom ci an nuwa mon bou.
\v 23 Na cori ma dike nyo yi nentiyeu, nubo na'ar wi yinen wo tum nure.
\v 24 Yaken kange nubo buro na nirum dor mwero kange ci na ya cinen dike a ta'a tiyeu, na ci carum dor cero. La nubo gwam an nyimom kero ci tok ti dor mwerue cierke. Ci an nyumom mon nii mo bwangten werfuner tiye.
\v 25 Dor nubo kumtacileu buro ne bilenkereu, nyon mulang cinen, nyon yici kero ki nyial, cia cokum dor cero, ki kulen do ci wab fulen do wiyeu. kange bwiyale, kange dike kwamiye, kange burotum.
\v 26 la Bulus tuu nubo, celfini con nirum dor cero kange ci, la cin yaken kuu wabe, na co yici dii ka kume nirka ciyeko. Co diye neka luma ko a ne ci tieyu.
\v 27 Kambo kumeni niber kiyan dimeu, Yhudawa buro Asiya to Bulus ku wabe, la cin bol nubo mwerkangum meu na tamco.
\v 28 Ci kwabang diroti nubo Israila ki tikang nyo won co nii wo merang nubo minti fiye gwammeu, dike ma kiyeti kange nubeu. werfuner, kange fiye wuro kebo kawo, la con bou ki Helenawa mor kuu wabe, la con yayamfiye cakcake wo.
\v 29 wori cin to Bulus wi kange Tarifima kange Bulus mor cinan lor ci kwati ki neer kange con bou ciko mor kuu wabe.
\v 30 La cinan loro a yilam ki dike, la nubo cwakang wari ya cin tam Bulus. cin kuuken co kuu wabe kale, la cin mangang yilokoti.
\v 31 Kambo ci cuiti na ci twalum ceri, fulen kwi lam niin dur nob kwenebo yico wursalima nubo cua tai ki kwalkanka ke.
\v 32 La Con tuu nenkwanebo kange nob bikwanebo cin cuu yiranken fiye nubo wiyeu. Kambo nubo to ni dur kwenebori, la cin dubom buka Bulus ce ko.
\v 33 La nii dur nob kwenebo yan lam tau Bulus, ki kom bwanco ki dukako yob. la cin me co ye mwa mane.
\v 34 Kangem mor nubo mwerumeu, tok keroti ki dimen. kambo nii durko kwenebo mani nyom bilenker tiyeri, la con toki ki a yaken ki Bulus fiye nangene.
\v 35 Kambo ci lam kwikari nob kwenebo tum co ker kwalkikwalki.
\v 36 La nubo ducce bwangten kwabang tiki dir a twalum co.
\v 37 Kambo Bulus darom na lam fiye nangeneri con yi nii dur cero ki man fiya nure nan yii nen ker ka? nii dur ko me co, moki tokum ki Helenaciya ka?
\v 38 Mwa kebo bwe masare wo kuma cum bwiye mo ter mwer kanka duwek nobek, mo tu nubo bikate na'ar mwa cuu ciko kiya?
\v 39 La Bulus ki min BaIsraile cinan loro Tarsus mor Cilicia min bwe bitine cinan loro dur. Ciyamen nan tokker kange nubowo.
\v 40 Kambo nii dur ko neco nure di, Bulus kenti dor fiye fuwa naa kung ken kang ceko dii wo nung ti cia kumangumeu, kambo fiye tam cineri, Bulus yi ci kero ki Ibraniyanci.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 Kebmibo kange tebmibo, kom nuwa kaka batiyo wo ma ka ti kumeneu.
\v 2 La kambo nubo mwerume nuwa Bulus yici kero ki nyi Ibraniyanci ri, la cin tam cinen, con toki.
\v 3 Min Ba Ibraniya ci bo Tarcus wo cili kili, kiya, la ma ma kiye kako fou mor cinanloro wo naar Gamaniel. Min fiya mwerum kambo ken dor bwangka mor bifumer tebbebo. min wiki ker bwangka kwamak, nawo gwam kumen ko nyo duweneu.
\v 4 Min ne dotange ki nure wo yaken ciko bwar, bwaka kange tunka lokuka, nabarub kange natub.
\v 5 Kambo wabe durko kange nubo durko a ne warketiye. Min yo mulang ka cinen dor kebbebo Dimascus, nan bwauci na bou ciko wursalima.
\v 6 La ki cin kakuke can nawofilanko dur lo kwama yoten nefilang ti.
\v 7 La man yarken bitine, la man nuwa diro yiye, Shawulu, Shawulu, ye bwi mwa neye dotangetiye?
\v 8 La man kari, “we mo Teluwe? la con yiye, co Yesu nazaret, wo mo ne dotange tiyeu.
\v 9 Nubo kange meu tom filanko, la ci nyombo dir nii woro yiye kereu.
\v 10 la min meco ye ma matiye Teluwe/ teluwse yiye kweni do ken mor Dimascus.
\v 11 La mani ma toti wori filanko wo yem nuwe miu. La nubo wari kange meu tamen kang ko ya kiye Dimascus.
\v 12 Wi ma nii dendo Anaiya, nii cwa tai kwama tifiye wer funer nii ken wo Ibraniyawa dam wiyeu gwam tok coti.
\v 13 Con bou minen, tii minen, la con man to co.
\v 14 La con yiye, kwama wo tebbebo ciyeu coknen na mo nyumom diker co cuitiyeu. Na tom nubo cak-cak, na nuwam diro ceruti nyiceu.
\v 15 wori mwan yikan nii warke ce nubo nin gwam ki dike mwa toweu kange wo mo nuwau.
\v 16 Na weu ye bwi mo ning tang tiye?
\v 17 Kambo ma yilaken wursalima la ma kwob diloti mor kuu waberi, la man yo dukum.
\v 18 Min to yi teti kwer wolum na dobum wursalima can candowu, wori mani cia ciya warker mwe dor minreti.
\v 19 La man toki Teluwe, ciki bwici nyumom kuwo man kurangi, man buk nubo buro ne bilenker dor mwerue mor bi kur wabero gwam.
\v 20 kambo bwiyale ni warke mweu Istifanus coreu, ma tim wi mati ciyai ma con kulen nubo buro do twalceu.
\v 21 La con yiye, ya wori man toum nen kutanfiye nubo kumtacile wiyeu.
\v 22 Cin cuwa tuu cinen lamna wo. la cin kung dir ciyero citi toki, atwalum wang nubeko wo dor bitiner la kebo dong-dong ca dam wi.
\v 23 Kambo ci kwabang diroti, ci mobang kuleng ciroti kange kung ka kwerek.
\v 24 Nii dur nob kwenibou, toki a dom ki Bulus fiye nangen nob kwenebo. La con toki a me coti ki mallika balyakye, wori co ki bwici na co nyumom ye bwi ci kwabnag dirtikercere.
\v 25 Kambo ci bwam co dii ki dukkari, Bulus yini bi kwane wo tim cinen, yori kabo werfun na tom nii wo barome wuro bulanko tacobeu?
\v 26 La kambo nii bikwaneu nuwa weri, la con yaken ni dur nob kwenebo nen yico ki “ye ko do ma ka tiye?” la nii wo Romaneu.
\v 27 La ni dur nob kwenebo bou la meci yiye mon Romanka bulus ciyaco, ki “Ong”.
\v 28 Nii dur nob kwenebo yi coki, kiyemero ducce matiyen yim bwebitineme. La Bulus yico, ci bou ye bwe roma.
\v 29 La nubo buro a meco kerti yeu dubangum co dang jang nii dur nob kwenebo cwam tai ken, kambo co nuwa Bulus bwe Ramon di, wori con bwam co di.
\v 30 Celfiniceri nii dur nob kwenebo cuiti na co nyumom bilenker dor dike yafudawa fi Bulus ti cikeu. La con kwim bwaka cko la con yi liya wabeu kange nob dir loro gwam na cin mwerkangi. la con yirau ki abulus yoken co tiber ciyer.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 Paul to nubo mwerume ri ki, minya yam kange kwam.
\v 2 Nii dur wabero wo coti ki Ananiya ne nubo bikwan gwam ciya kwanice.
\v 3 Dila Paul yi co ki, “Kwama an kwanne mo nii bwir moyim namo mamen warke ki bolang ka, dila moki ciya kwaye ki kang wo kebo dong-dong kange bolang?”.
\v 4 Nubo tirangum wiyeu ki ye bwi mon torang nii dur nob waber kwama ro tiye?
\v 5 Paul yiki, Yimi ma yombo miki nii dur, molangum molange ki, mani mwa tok bwirang kerti nii dur nubo lokume.
\v 6 La kambo Bulus nyomom kange win bwe Saduciyawa, la con tok kero ki luma wi ki, kebmibbo min nii Farisawa, bibwe farisawa kambo min cuiti na nyomom kwenka ceko tuwe wo man ma bolang cekeu.
\v 7 kambo ca tok nye ri, kwabkang ka bwi bwitici. Farisawa kange Sadukawa kange, mwerenkang kako wo.
\v 8 Sadukawa toki ki, Kwenka mani, bibei tomange mani, yuwatangbeko mani, La nii farisawa nyom gwam.
\v 9 Kwobkang kako kweni wi bwiti cii, la Farisawa ki ciya to bo dikero bwir fou nii wo nen. Ye a bwiti no yuwa tangbeko toker kange co kaka no Bibei tomangeceu toker kange cori.
\v 10 Kambo kwobkang kako dur kweni tiber cereri, nii dur nob kwenebbo cwam tai ki kari ci wobrangum Bulus, ki fiti kang cek, la cin dok kwenebo na yira tou co ki bikwan tiber nob durembo na bou ki co fiye ca fiyam corka tiyeu.
\v 11 Kambo kume kange lauweri, kwama tii cungya cek toki ki, “cware tai cin cuwa nen firen Ursalima naweu. Mwan nii kange fou Roman.
\v 12 kambo fini celum ri, kangum yahudawa ma nero bwir laci nacin co dor ciyero nin chilka ki weri, naci chare kaka, ci no diker no ci twalum Bulus ri, nimde.
\v 13 Nubo cum kwini na'ar wo yi yimbo bwirko weu.
\v 14 La cin ya ni dur wabero nen kange nubo durko ki, Bin yo dorbero fiye chilka no ba twalbo Bulus diker mani wo ba matiye.
\v 15 Na weu bi yi Liya wabero na bou ki co fou bitine na bin fiya co ki dikero bwir ka ceri, cin ciya na twalum co.
\v 16 kambo bibwe hadace bwe bubiya nuwa na weri la ya yi Bulus ki,
\v 17 “Bulus cho kange nii win na ya ki nii wo dur bero nen cin wi ki dike ca toktiye.
\v 18 Nii wo tim wiyeu tuu bwewo yaciko fiye dur nub wabero wiyeu ki Bulus wo fou mor furcina, cin yiki ki nyon bou ki co monen cin wiki dike ca toktiye.
\v 19 La nii dur nub waber tou co doken mor, la me co ki “Ye mon cuiti namon yi yere?”
\v 20 Bwewo yi ki, “Yahudawa ciya ki bouki Bulus fine fiye mwerkangka, cin cuiti na me co diker dor bolnag ceko nen.
\v 21 Dila necire cou, nubo wi cum kwini naar wo ci cwiti nacin twallum ceu. Cin yiyim bou wo ciki mani ciya chati, mani ciya noti, kambo ci twalum ceri nimde ci chachari. Bwen naweu, ciki bati ci ning tang diker mwa tok tiyeti.”
\v 22 La nii dur wabero yici ki kom manki kange diker wo ka yii nii wo tiyeu, nii wo yimco dikero gwam.
\v 23 La con cou nob bikwanebo yob ki, ciya cok nob bikwanebo bikwate yob nacin yaken ki co Caesarea, kange nub tuwabbo kwini niber, kange nubo bikate kwini yob, ciya kwenum ki kume taar rewo.
\v 24 Con yici ki ciya dou bicirdo wo Bulus a fuhtiye na yaken ki con loh kwarer.
\v 25 La con mulang bifumer nawo ki.
\v 26 Claudius Lysias kimo liyar kalero nen Felix, yarum nen ti.
\v 27 Nii wo Yahudawa tam co, la cin cuiti nacin twalum co. kambo bou cinen ki nub bikwaneb, la man cokceu. min yumom ciki no biten Romane.
\v 28 Min cuiti na yunmom diker wo ci tok ti dor cereu. La min ya ki con fiye mwerkang ka.
\v 29 Min nyom ci merang co kerti wo yilam na doka ceu. La cin manki diker wo yilam ciya twalum coti, ko ciya tung coti furcina.
\v 30 Di la cin yiye ciki, dikero bwirko wi wo ci cwiti na cin ma nii wo nineu, la dangjang min tung kenco monen min toki diker ci ficoti cikeu ciya bou ciko fiye mou wiyeu. Ya kwamer.
\v 31 La nob bikwanebo bwang ten diker cha tikeu. Cin bou ki Bulus ki bikume fou Antipatris.
\v 32 Kambo kume lauweri nub bkwanebo dubom nob tuwab bo kange cou. lan cin yilanken ce loh.
\v 33 Kambo nub tuwabbo lam Caesarea ri, cin nee takada wii liyar bitinenen, Cin neken ten Bulus cinen.
\v 34 Kambo liya bitine tou takada ri, Ye bouki Bulus feh? coki no biten Cilicia.
\v 35 Con yiki “Man nuwa nen gwam kambo nubo wo toker tidor mwereu bouri, Con toki ki, ciya yaken ki co kan Liya dur bitenero nen Hiridus firen wabkang ka.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Ki kume nundi, Nii kange wii ciyi cotike ananiya nii dur wabe, kangum nubo dur kange nob yob ka bolange decero, Tertullus yaken wi ki kiyange Bulus ce. kabum nii dur bitineronen.
\v 2 Ki kwama wo Bulus tim kabum nii liyar Tertullus yoten torank coti kiwe gwamna “Ker mwer nyo fiya, yiblume to kaba, bo ki yulka bitine ben.
\v 3 Dike mo maneri nyo ki bukan kangen, nii dur Felis.
\v 4 Kali nene do tange, miki nanneti nuyen bi dom nan yinen ker.
\v 5 Cin fiyam nii wo kan dikeroti kilanye yila cuk nubo Yahudawa kalenen gwam. ciya terkutumeti.
\v 6 Mani naco fuyatamin kuwaber, co dike nyo teuce (Nyo cuiti na nyo warcinen wo dong dong kange funereu.
\v 7 Dila Lysias boyoco win kibi gwan kanciyen.
\v 8 Na mume Bulus dikero wo gwam di mwan yumom dike nyi tok ti dorcereu.
\v 9 Yahudawa ciya bwanten ci, chin ciya chiko ki dong dong.
\v 10 Ki kwama wo nii dur ko ne Bulus filanko na tok kereri, Bulus ciya, “Miyumom ki coti kila mwin nii warke bitinewo nen, ki bilangtum mi nung dor miro ti munen.
\v 11 Mon yumom cubo kumeni kwob cillombo yob ciko min kwi nami ma wabka mor Ursalima.
\v 12 Kambo ci fiyaye mor bikur wabereu, ma kwobkang bo kange nii kange, ma kung bo kiyan tiber nuber mor bi kur wabe, kaka, cinan lor.
\v 13 Mani ciya nung mwen bilenke dike ci toyeti cikeu.
\v 14 Dila miyinen, mor dikerowo ci toki kuwabe nyoken mi bwangten kwama nen kwanimin. mine dur mor dike ci mulang mor bifumer durko.
\v 15 Min wiki bi kwan nener naceu ken Kwama nen, na nubo buro, fuloka ko bwareu wi, ki nubo cak-cakeu kange nubo bwir gwam.
\v 16 La kang-kang miki mani nami to nermiro kuwayebo, kabum Kwamam, kange niffir.
\v 17 kangum cotinim mi bou nan tinkan kume diker cike kange lumanerer.
\v 18 Min tu nyo ner mir mani nyo la yahudawa biten asiay dikero moten wo cenge ku wabe kebo ki mwer kanka ki kutume.
\v 19 daten nubo bulum ciye bo fiye mo wiyeu duwen naci wiki diker tokka dor mwer.
\v 20 na kebo nyori nubo lominbo ciya togki na ci fiye kidire kikwamawo matogti kabum nob mwerkanka Yahudawa.
\v 21 No dor dikewo mi tokki ki dir kabum ciyeu, wori gwamka nob Bwerem. cimen coti ci doti naci moten bolanko.
\v 22 Felis, wo ci yimco ker dor nureroweu, kungum nuwa kako. Cin yi ki, “No Lysias nii dor, nub kwenebo, yirau Ursalimari, man tok diker amati ki bolang mweko neneu.
\v 23 La co yi nii bikwan ne nob kwenebbo ayoken Bulus kan nob corkab, la co fiya cerka biduwar kati kange mor ferubceb fiyabo nure aneco diker ci cwitiyeti.
\v 24 Kambo Kumeni kange cumeri, Filibus kange wice Duruskila, wo Bayahudiya La cin twomi na cin bouki Bulus di naci nuwa cinen ker bilenker dor Almasiya Yeesu.
\v 25 Di la kambo Bulus bulangi kange co, dor cak-cake, taka dorek, kange bolang ko boutiyeu, Felis cwam tai, La yiki, “Muyaken ti naweu. Dila non fiya filang ki bwiri, min twom mwen.”
\v 26 Ki kwama wo cun nyoti nerwi ki Bulus a neco kemer ducce kir-kir naco tok ker kange co.
\v 27 Ki cwuro yob Borkiyas Festas yilam nii dur buwab Filibus, wori ciki do fuwor bwiyat fiye Yahudawa yoten to Bulus ki toka.
\c 25
\p 
\v 1 La Festus do ki kume taar gwam kaisariya yaken Ursalima.
\v 2 La nii dur wabe kange nubo dur yahudawa cin bo ki kwanere dor Bulus cer, la cin kenco.
\v 3 Cin me tikali cinen na ci doken Bulus mor dotange - di Festus na cou Bulus Ursalima ri na cin twalumco dor nure
\v 4 Dila Festus ciya ciki, Bulus bou firen kaisariya, kutakni coki bweco aniylareken firen.
\v 5 Nyori wo Ayumom bwikan gekotiyeri. Na bwirank ke kange we kange nii wori ciya toco.
\v 6 Dila ki kume narub kaka kwob la nyilake kaisariya. Celfini ceri Nyiken fiye bworange ki ciya bwoki Bulus kabum cem.
\v 7 Kambo Bulus boweri Yahudawa wo Ursalima tirangum bidom ci yoten ci bwerauti ki kiyage laci fiyabo ken wi.
\v 8 Bulus cokum dorcero ki, ma mabo nii nen bwiranke, kaka Yahudawa, kaka kuwabe kaka kaisar.”
\v 9 Dila Festus ki do fuwor bwiyarade fiye Yahudawa wiye, Dila nyori co me Bulus ki mo cuiti namo ya Ursalima.
\v 10 Bulus yiki co tim fiye maka borank kaisar fiye tam ceu. Min ma dike yorbei kom nyumom gwam.
\v 11 Na bicom mima burankge mima dike dateng bwerangke mikobo in bwiyam. dila na dike lam na bitoren cwerke nin, nikange cunkange. mi tuwciurkumeti fiye kaisar.”
\v 12 kambo Festus dim fuwakangkako kange nobe ri La ciya ki, mo cu kaisar monyanken kaisar”.
\v 13 Ki kume kange, liya Agrippa kange Bernice cin yirau Caeserea na cin yacuner Festus ki diker.
\v 14 La lam kumeni, kila Festus nyi liya keti bidarange wo Filibus domti mur kuu kuka.
\v 15 Ki kwamawo mi Ursalima, kange dur ni wabka kange nubo dur Yahudawa ci boki kiyange ce fiye miwiyeu, cin keni naci twalumco.
\v 16 Ki woro yi ciki, ke dam Romawa yibo ki aneken bibei nii bibwiyer, La wo ci kwakiyagece cin neco firank naco congum dorcero nob kiyagecenen, naco kiye ker kiyangece.
\v 17 La ciin mwelim kebo ki tiranka kene, celfiniceri miyiken fiye maka bolange minyici ciya boki nii co.
\v 18 Kambo nob kiyangebo boki kyangeceri, kero ken mani morece.
\v 19 Miyumom kwaka kaciyeko na kuwaabece dor Yesu wo bwiyamdi Bulus ki wuki dume.
\v 20 Mi fwiki kambo ma fuma kerowo matongti lami meco miki monyaken Ursalima na walum kero.
\v 21 Dila Bulus do ciya toco, Kaisar walum kero lamitoki ciya yobco men tukco kaisar nen.
\v 22 Agrippa yi Festus, Min cuiti na nuwa nii wo.” “Fini,” Festus yiki, “Mwan nuwa co.”
\v 23 La ki celfiniceri Agrippa kange Bernice cin bou ki diker chaklang ka, kange nubo durko bitineceu. La Festus toki, ki ciya cokum Bulus fiye ciweyeu.
\v 24 Festus yiki Liya Agrippa kange nubo wi kange ciyeu cin toh nii wo kange nubo mwerum feu nub Yahudawa kange coh Ursalima gwam ci werang coti ki daten bo co yim ki dume.
\v 25 ma nyumom mabo bwirang ke daten bwere, Dila wori co twalum kero cou yaken cuko fiye kaisar wiyeu. Nyori ma motum intomken co.
\v 26 Di miman ki Kerokange mitontiye miki murank kaisar nen. tomange, ki kerowo mibocuko kakumeu, nawonyon mitonentiyeu mo liya Agrippa. nan fiyam dike mayuktanti muranka mikonen dorcer.
\v 27 Fiye miwiyeu Bwira kabo intunin bwiranke mi murankbo bwirang ke co.
\c 26
\p 
\v 1 La agrippa yi Bulus, “Mon nyam coka doremwei la Bulus kunkan ceko yoten condorceroti.”
\v 2 Miki Fuwor nerer, liya Agrippa, ki kerowo yahudawa bouti cuko dor mireu.
\v 3 Nyori mo nii yumka mor den Yahudawa kange yabciebo. Nyori mikenenti. Nyoli bob nermwero kange bwewo.
\v 4 Miyi komti gwam yahudawa yubram fiye yim kallemibo fiye wucakke kange Ursalima.
\v 5 Cin yubrangum ye ki kaba, daten ciya yumom miyiyen na bafarasawa.
\v 6 Naweu miki naci mamen bolang nawo wori nor wa kwama tu tebbyebbo ni nen.
\v 7 Wo cou nure ber gero kwab curomboyo yoti ner wiye. ciya wou ki kwamawo ci wabkwamati ki nero win fiye kwama wiyeu kakum kange kume. Ki yoka nerewa, Liya agrippa, yahudawa buranti.
\v 8 Ye bwikange aburank ti ki diker yumanko kwama akun nob bweyame?
\v 9 La mi burankge ki maka dikero kiden Yesu bana zaret.
\v 10 Min ma buranka mor Ursalima, mi ku nob bwika kwamako duce mor Fursuna. Ki bikwan do wo mifiya fiye nob dur wabero wiyeu, kange wo ci twerciti mineci mwerka duwen.
\v 11 neci dotange duce kwab kuh wabe mi cuti nan dongcinen naci ma burkane. Ma ma kiye ciren kangeci minaci dotange yaken cuka bitiye tim bokage.
\v 12 Ki kwamawo mima buroka boti mi yaken Dimaskus ki ciyaka dur nob wabe.
\v 13 Mor yame mi, ki kaku, mo liya mito firen dikawama wo la kaku filanken filanko ketenye, kange nubo nyo yakenti wari.
\v 14 Kabom kwaob nyo yarken bitine, minuwa diro kange tok keroti kange mwoh ki nye Ibranciyawa yiti ki, shawulu, Shawulu ye bwi mon neye dotange tiye? bwikabo na kundike cucuwe.
\v 15 La miki webo teluwe? Teluwe ciya mo Yesu wo mone dotange.
\v 16 Naweu kwen titiye ki co kerowo manun dor miro munenen nan yome? na yilam canga kange nii warkere dor dike moyume dormireu nawo kange wuro miyinentiye. fokab.
\v 17 Man cuken fiye nobo wiye kange nubo ma to ci fiye mowiyeu.
\v 18 Na mo wumom nuwage ciyeu yilau ki ci kumtacile yilau ki ci filank. na cin fiya cerka fiye yuwako bwirko wiyeu na ci you yuwa kwama, kange fuloka dikero bwir nen wo cha ne nubo bwang ten co tiyeu.
\v 19 La nyori, liya Agrippa miken kom kangumbo ki dukumbo wamito dikwamau.
\v 20 Dila, kabokoce buro mor Dimaskus. kange Ursalima kange biten Yahudawa gwam, kange nob furenebo, mima cinen bwiranke naci yiloten fiye kwama wiyeu, cin ma dike daten yilokau.
\v 21 Co dike bwi yahudawa ci tamce mor kuh wabe ci cuiti naci twalum co.
\v 22 Kwama tikang wo duwin mi tim kabum bibei kange nubo dur, warke dor dike annabawa kange Musa toki abwitiye.
\v 23 Dong dong Almasiya a nuwa dotange anyi lam kaba wociyar komti bwere an tok filang fiye yahudawa kange nubo yumbo kwama.
\v 24 Kambo Bulus dim coka duwek cekori, Festus tok kero ki dir, ki Bulus twaka mani ki nyomka mweka donen twalka.
\v 25 Dila Bulus yico, “mitwalbo nii dur Festus kibi kwan nerer mi tok bilenke tiye kange cinen.
\v 26 Wori liya yum bo dike burombo gwam, co dike bwi mitok keroti kibi kwane, wori miyom dike kange mani wo yurangum yurange.
\v 27 Mo ne bilenke kange nob tomange dukumbo, ko liya agrippa? mi nyomom mo ne bilenke.
\v 28 Agrippa ni yi Bulus mor kere biduware muki cui namo bwolye na yilam nii bwanka kwama ka?
\v 29 Bulus yiki “miki nanenti kwama, mor kene bi dure kange kene dur, kebo mo ki kwama, gwam kange nubo nuwa yilam na mo.
\v 30 Liya kweni ti kange nubo dur kange Bernice, kange nubo gwam yilamom kange.
\v 31 kambo ci dubom ku wabe ri cin ter tok kako kere ko bwiti ci ciki, “Nii wo mabo dike dotange borom kange bwika.”
\v 32 Agrippa yi Festus ki naki niwo tumbo kiyage yakenbo cuko kaisar nadi noci yamkancinen.
\c 27
\p 
\v 1 Bwiko ciyaka ko ki nyiki yang italiya ciin neken kange nubo kangembo furcina kang nii dur nub kwenebo ci co ti yuliya wo mor mwan Agustus ke.
\v 2 Nyin doken nabire mwenge mor Adramatiya, wo ywel bwiti na cii ya bidom kange cunga wima ko Anciya. La nyi yaken mor wima Aristakus wo Tasalonika mor Makidoniya cin yaken kange nyo.
\v 3 Cel fini ceri nyi yiram cinanlor sidom, fiye wo Yuliyas nung Bulus nin neer lumare la cin dobco naci ya farub cebo nen di naci yo toka ceko.
\v 4 Nyi kweni wiri nyin doken mor Wima ri nyon yaken kong mwenge kubruce, wori yuwa ko ne nyo dotange ti.
\v 5 Ki kwama nyi yabken wima nyi yabken dinge kilikiya kange Bamfiliya nyim la mira, cinan loro Liciya.
\v 6 Wii niii nabire nob kwenebo fiya nabire mwenge wo bou Takendariya ri, a yaken ti Italiya cin more ce.
\v 7 Kambo nyi yakenti kumeni kila nyi yaken biluma, la ki cuile gwam ri nyin lam ki dotange bidom kange cinindu ri la yuwa ko dob nyo bo tak nanyi bwangten cunga ko cou, nyin yaken cunga ko ci kicimkice bidom kange karita bidom kange Salmani.
\v 8 Nyi yaken cunga konge ki dotange, nyimde nyi bow fiye kange cou ti ki fiye turangka ko ken, wo bidom kange la ciya.
\v 9 na weu nyin tu kumeni kila, la kwama ngag ngake Yuahadwa cum, la naweu yambo yilam ki tai la Bulus werang ci
\v 10 Ciki, Nubo matori yambo wo bi ter tiyeu atin yilam ki nuwa ka twirak kange le-ka dikerek duce, kebo kawo kwilendo ceu kange nabire mwenge, dila kange dume beuken.
\v 11 La nii na bire nub kwenebo cuwa tu ka diiir teluwe kange nuu nabire mwengeko nin la cuwa bo ker Bulus cero nin.
\v 12 Wori fiye tuka kwilenek na bire mwenge ko bwei yim wiki cukakiya ri nob kwobka nabire mwengeko duce tok ki ciya dubom fiye cou la tano cwika fiyaka ri bi lam cinar lo finikiya, nabi yim (wa kiyauwi). La finikiya co fiye tii mwe nabire mwnege mor karita, wo to kwasalmen ti kange mar to me tiye.
\v 13 Kambo yuwa bange ko ter cu kako kibi luma ri, nubo kwob nabire mwenge ko tiyeu kwabi neer cer ki ciin fiyam dikero cii cwi tiyeu. Dila ciin cukum duka nabirek mwnegeko la ciin bwangten cunga ko karita bidom kange kong mwenge ko
\v 14 La fiyaco bi duwar di yuwako kwani nyeu wo cii cuwa tiki yuro kilidom yoten buk nyo ti diyelenen.
\v 15 kambo nabire mwengeu fweki cukako fiye ki yuwa wori yuwa ko lambi kwan ceredi, nyin bwang ten nur yuwau.
\v 16 La nyin bwnagten fiye nyi fiyam cerka ko diyele bi duware coti ki kauda, la ki dotange nyi bwam nabire bi duware bwi durko nen.
\v 17 Kambo cii kongum nabire mwenge bi duware dii yeri, ciin ma nangen ki duka ceko ri ciin bwam bwi nabireko durko cuko. Taito tamci ki cukum dikero a tam nabire ti dor mwengere dila nyin bwang tenti.
\v 18 Nyin nuwa dotange ducce ki yuwa mwengek wo ki celfiniceri ciin ter cutangka kwileneko wo mor nabire mwengenen wii.
\v 19 Ki kume taar ri nob nangenebo mor nabire mwengeu cutang kwilendo mor mnabire wi ki kang cek.
\v 20 kambo nyi to bo filang kakukek kaka bitiren kume taare ri, yoka nereko ki nyan fiya ceer kau cerum nyinen.
\v 21 kambo cii ya yambo kwitan cari mani yeri, Bulus kweni tiber nob nangeneb nabire mwengeko ri ciki, “nubo, nakin kom cuwa tu kermiro nen, bi kwenu bo karitari no biki fiyabo twirako buro kange leka kwileko.
\v 22 Na weu miyi komnti ko yilam ki birom nerem wori nii mania bwiyati more kume dila ka nabire mwenge bi lem tiye.
\v 23 wori wo min naceu, wo mi wabti takeu bwe tomange ceu tii cunga miik.
\v 24 La ciki cware tai, Bulus tam nyo mwanti kabum kaisar re. la to, kwama mor jire duwece neken gwam nubo wo yaken wari kange mweu.
\v 25 La nyori ko yilam k bikwan neeret nubo, wori min ne bilenke kwama nen atin yilam nawo ci yiyereu.
\v 26 La batin cwa bi kangtangi kange Island.
\v 27 Kambo kume kwobcilombo naareu dimeri, la cii tung nyo fou kange firen mor wima ko adriyate, ki ciin kume ri nubo fu nabire mwenge tiyeu kwabi ki ciin dadum kange bitine Kange.
\v 28 Kambo cii cuwa ri, cii fiya nako kwini yob kambo kakten biduwar di ci cuwa ten di nako kwob cilumbo nung.
\v 29 Cin tum tai ki kangeri ciyan kwiti teer, la ciin curken duka ko ciin komti cikeu naar cwile nabire mwenge nen, cin kwob dilo fini a celum wulom.
\v 30 Nob nangeneb nabire mwengebo do nure ciya dubom nabire tiye ri ciin merken nabire mwengeu biduwareu mor wima. ciin mani namwi ci yan merangken duka ko kangembo wo mor nabire mwenge kabum nabire ko nen.
\v 31 Dila Bulus yi nii dur nob kwenebo kange tangum cembo “No nubo buro mani a tim ti mor nabire, msni ciys fiya cerka ti.”
\v 32 Dila nob kwenebo mwatum dukako cinn dubti yuram.
\v 33 Kambo fini ter celkakeri Bulus kenci gwam cia can carito. ciki Diye wo co diye kwobcillumbo naareu wo kom mor curka, la kom cabo cari.
\v 34 La mi kinong komti, kom cam carito wori cerka kume ko lam, kange kume mani wiin wo a le yere dore cetiye”.
\v 35 Bwiko ci tok kero wari ciin tu carito la ciin bu kwama nen kang, ciin duwa carito cin yo cakako.
\v 36 Dila gwam ce ciin fiya bikwan neret ri ciin tu carito ken.
\v 37 Nubo kwini kwob yob turdo kwini niber cilumbo nuukkun ki dume tini nabire mwenge nen.
\v 38 Kambo cica ci bwameri, cin filam ten ki nabire mwengeu,
\v 39 Kambo fini celumeri ci nyombo bitineu dila ciin to kum ki konge la ciin tokkangi bwiti no ci yan yila ki nabire mwengeu wiri.
\v 40 La ciin mwatum duka ceko ri ciin dobti mor wima. ki kwama co wiin ciin kwim dukako, yila nabire tiyeu. Dila nabire mwengeu kwiti dor yabum cerum cereu. kambum cembo ywiken wi, la mor kwita kako mani la bi kwan mwelka mani.
\v 41 cin bou fiye wo cajiyo yob mwerkangummeu, la na bire mwenge doken mor yabume. Tangum nabire mwengeu ywiken wi la mani yayamti, La cunga ko ki kyarangi ki mwembo mwelangtieu.
\v 42 La nob kwenebo ci naci twallum nob furcinabo kari kange kwa mwembo cwalem.
\v 43 dila nii dur cero cwi naci cer ki Bulus la cin tim ki dikero cii cui makau, nubo nyumom kwaka mwengek la cin mwabken mor mwenge cin yabken konge.
\v 44 Dila tangnum bayilobo na bwangten kange dor bwatiyer kangembo dor nabire nen. Ki nurewo, la gwam nye nyin beken kwamer bitine.
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 Fiya cuwo nya yilau kwamere, nyan nuwa den diiyele cuwa ki malta.
\v 2 Nubo mwan loro cuwa nung yinen luma nerek cin nuwa nyinen kira, cin yuwo nyo gwam ker mwemer kange cwuii ngir-ngireu.
\v 3 La Bulus mwer bwatiye yo ti kirari, kwentibe ceru, wori kirako cwillen cakkan cinen ti kang.
\v 4 La nubo mwan loro cuwo to na cuwe yayim kang cek ri, ci tokkangti bwitici ki, “Nii wo nii twal nob ti ci cuku mor bware caji. Kero dong dongeu ciyabo nii a buuti.”
\v 5 La con waciken na cuwe kira, kii cobo.
\v 6 Ci nintanti na ci to bwici fum, ki kwirum bwi na yarke bitine na bwiyam. La cin to co fiya kutangi, cin tobo diker fiya cobo di, cin fulongum ner cero, cin yi ki con bwel.
\v 7 La bi dom kange fiye cuwe, take kange wi na nii durece diiyele cuwa, wo ci cuwo ti Babiliya yuwo nyo, ki luma nerek, tam nyo na kume taar ce.
\v 8 La te Babiliya cokkati kiwirum bwi kange teka fiya cuwa Bulus ya cinnen kwob cinen dilo, cin yoti kang dor cer con twam co.
\v 9 Bwiko dike woro bwiyeu tangne nube yim diile diile wuro nen nuba. Luma cin bou ken cin twam ci.
\v 10 Nubo wuro ne nyo dur ti ki dur. La nyon ka bati yamtiri, cin ne nyo dike nyo cwitiyeu.
\v 11 Bwiko cwak ko taare nyong kwen yambo ki nabire mwenge wo ma tirako wiiye, nsbire Alexandriya, ki bwel do yob ci ywellum tikab dore cike.
\v 12 Bwiko nya yiram cinanr lor ciranku nyon yim wii kume taar.
\v 13 Wii ri nyon yaken cinan lor Rigiyum ki kume wiin di, yuwa ko bangeu kwenu, la mor kume yobeu nyin lam cinan lor, Butiyoli,
\v 14 Nyon fiya yitub nyebo kange wii, cin cuwo nyong yii kange ci kume niber, nure wo nya yaken Roma.
\v 15 Nyo firen di yitub nyebo nuwa fulen nyero cin ceru cin yuwo nyo, tati fiye miyeka dike Abiya kange bituk taar. La Bitrus to yitubori, con fiya bikwan neret.
\v 16 Kambo nya doken Roma ri, cin dob Bitrus na yi ki kwace kange nii kwene wo to co tiye.
\v 17 Ki kume taar di Bulus cuwo nubo wuro na dur mor Yahudawa. La cin bou ri, con yiki, “yitub me, ma mabo nob nen dikero bwir kaka, dike ka ciya cike wo tembebo ceu, cin taye. Bwiko cin me ya, ci cwiti naci nyam kang minen ci fiya yebo ki bwirangke wo lam twalka.
\v 18 Kambo cii merang ye kereri, cin cwi na cin nyemkan minen, wori ci fiya yebo ki bwirang ker wo lam ciya twalye tiye.
\v 19 La Yahudawa tok diker cwika nerek ciyeu, cin dok ye, ya ki kiyange kaisar nin, muni bou ki kiyange bitineu.
\v 20 Dor kerero wo ma cuwo kom na to kom na yi kom. Nyo neri Israila ci bwam yere.
\v 21 La cin yi co “nya yuwobo tomange kange Yahudawa dor mwer kaka kange yitubo bou bo nyi nyo dikero bwir dor mwer.
\v 22 Nyo wcii na yi nuwa muneng ye mo kwatiye dor mwan nibero wo, wori nyon nyimom dike wuro cin toki fiye gwam.
\v 23 cin yo cinen kakuko, nubo ducce bou fiye ci yim wiye con yi ci dikero gwam, con yi cerka liyar kwama, con ken ci dor Yesu ter ti ki Musa ya ciko nob tomangeb ki buri mee doti.
\v 24 Kangum bo ciya dike co tokkeu, kangumbo ne bo bilenke.
\v 25 La cin ciya kambo kange butici, Bwiko Bulus dim kere di cin cu. “Yuwa tangbeko wusakke tok ker nyii Ishaya nii tomange teb kimeb bo nin.
\v 26 Yi ki “ya nubo wuro nen, na yi ci,” ki nuwaka, kan nuwa, la ma ka nyomti, ki toka kan to, maka nyomti.
\v 27 wori ner nibero wuro kuci, ki tuci, bwai naci nuwa, cin kumom nuwe ciye, naci tore ki nuwe ciye, ci nuwa ki tu ci nyimom ki ner cer, na ci yilau na twam ci.
\v 28 Nyori kon nyimom fuloka kwamako, cin ya nubo nyumbo kwama, ciya nuwa.
\v 29 La co tokum dike buro di yahudawau kweni, cu lor ki kwobkanka ko dur more ciye.
\v 30 Bulus yii wi ki chor kambo co co yim loh Aya, cin wab nubo gwam wo bou cineneu.
\v 31 La ci tok liyar kwamaro ti, ci meran dikero dor Yesu ti kibi kwamer neret ci ywa cobo wii. 
